title: OneDay for Senior Living
description:
OneDay, a prompted question-and-answer video app that allows senior living communities to capture their resident's life stories.

Features:
- Easily create high quality, branded, videos and share them online.
- Automatically share with family members via email and text message. 
- Marketing capabilities that improve your sales team's ability to communicate with potential customers.
- World class customer service!

recentChanges: - Updates for Android 11.
comments: When the app works it creates really great videos and memories. However, it takes forever to upload and save, won't allow me to transfer videos from my phone, and since the update yesterday, it freezes as soon as I hit record. My job requires me to use this app very regularly so it would be nice if it worked better on Samsung Galaxy.
Works Great! Very easy to use and learn. You may want to look at compatibility for Android 11 coming up soon because the app is broken on the beta, but I can't blame you for that it's my fault!
Would like to sign in on a desktop or laptop to edit instead on the phone
When it works, it's great

title: Senior Living Finder
description:
Find the right senior community for your loved one. With the FREE Senior Living Finder app, you’ll save time browsing and tracking personalized community referrals from a real local advisor.

YOUR SEARCH SIMPLIFIED

 - Explore communities with photos, reviews, and details.
 - Book tours 
 - Keep track of your personal notes and ratings.
 - Browse communities referred just for you.
 - Access your advisor for quick answers.

A PEOPLE POWERED APP

Once you create your account, a senior living advisor listens to your loved one’s needs and goes to work choosing from our nationwide network of over 17,000 select communities. Browse photos and reviews of options hand­ selected by your advisor. When you see a community you like, book a tour (on your schedule) within the app. Then track your visits with your own in-app notes and ratings.

IT’S EASY AND FREE

Support and guidance are always just a tap away with the handy senior living advisor call button. Plus, the app and the service cost you nothing. We’re paid by our partner communities only if you move in.

CONNECTING FAMILIES TO SENIOR LIVING

Since 2000, A Place for Mom has guided families through the senior care maze. Today we provide peace of mind to over 200,000 families each year. Our knowledgeable and compassionate advisors are dedicated to helping you find senior living you can feel great about.

COMMITTED TO CARE AND QUALITY

We understand. No two families are the same, and no two senior housing circumstances are the same. That’s why A Place for Mom (and Dad too!) prioritizes personalized service with a team of trained and caring senior living experts. We listen closely to provide recommendations that account for your family circumstances, location, cost concerns, and medical factors.

TAILORED TO YOU

Finding senior living for a loved one can be both emotional and technically daunting without compassionate, knowledgeable assistance. Our senior living advisors are trained to understand the most delicate matters of elder care, including nursing home qualifications, dementia care, types of assisted living, VA benefits, and senior care payment options.

A NETWORK OF CARING

Our network of senior care community partners undergo careful review of licenses, inspection reports, and public information. We count on our customers to provide ongoing reviews and ratings both before and after move in. We want to know that we’re making recommendations you can feel good about.

title: Realtime Senior Living Update
description:
With our Update app, you quickly update your availability so you are visible to all searching in "real-time" 24/7, right from your smartphone or iPad.

We Offer:
An easy to use innovative app that will:
--  Showcase your facility on our map and search results
--  Shows picture, room availability, care options, starting price and if you accept Medicaid for payment.
--  Prioritizes search results based on criteria selected by the searcher (Care, location, pricing, room type, respite care, memory care, accept Medicaid, etc)
--  Provides phone number, address and directions for searchers to directly connect with you!!
--  Track the number of searches for your facility

Your Benefits:
1. Low-cost, high-return marketing resource
2.  Your valuable time recovered as your site availability is always up to date and searchable
3.   Used by Hospitals, Skilled Nursing Facilities, Rehabs, hospices, case managers, placement professionals, fiduciaries, and more - anyone can search for free.
4.  Direct connection to you, with no referral fee paid to Realtime Senior Living!
5.  Marketing material for you to share with your referral sources to let them know they can "Find us Here" in "Realtime"

Ensure your care home or community is visible, up-to-date and included in all future searches!

title: Philips Cares for Senior Living
description:
Be there for your community
 
Philips Cares for Senior Living is a cloud-based resident safety and community management system.  The Philips Cares for Senior Living Mobile Community Dashboard provides senior living community operators with a clear view of resident activity with 24/7 real-time monitoring. 
 
The Mobile Community Dashboard app can only be used as part of the Philips Cares for Senior Living system, which incorporates wearable devices for both staff and residents. 
 
App features include:
- Real-time location on community maps
- Resident alerts notifications through the Action Center
- Ability to manage and re-assign wearables devices
- Chat features that allow staff and management to quickly communicate
- Up-to-date community events and announcements through the Announcements page
- Step count activity monitoring through the Step Count Leaderboard
 
Philips Cares for Senior Living is part of the Philips Cares solution family, which together empower at-risk seniors and their professional and family caregivers across independent living and senior living communities to help make sure the right care is provided at the right time.
 
Want to learn more? Visit us at www.lifeline.philips.com/business/cares-for-senior-living

title: Realtime Search
description:
Your Direct Connection to Available Options

Are you searching for available senior living?
Realtime makes searching simple & fast with our innovative solution. View available options in ‘Realtime’ that meet your patient, client, or loved one’s needs based on the criteria you choose – with immediate and future availability.

Realtime Search App Benefits:

1.  Quick, easy-to-use search, including:
    a.  Care provided, location, pricing, room type, respite care, accept Medicaid for payment
    b.  Directly connect to homes and communities (phone number, address, and driving directions)
2.  Search results contain: picture, state license, and key information
3.  Realtime availability – saves time searching for available rooms
4.  Not a placement agency nor do we collect any fees for referrals to the homes or communities
5.  No personal information is required or collected – search anonymously at no cost

So simple and easy to use.  It takes minutes to search instead of hours and days.  Now you can focus more time on reviewing the options that meet your needs, and less time calling options that don't.

Note:  Realtime Senior Living does not endorse or recommend any options.  Please do your due diligence, and visit the option to find the perfect fit for you.

title: The Independent Daily Edition
description:
Subscribe to The Independent Daily Edition, which features all the award-winning journalism from our newspaper, designed for a premium digital experience on your device.
 
Keep-up-to date with the latest breaking global headlines as well as articles, analysis and opinion from our award-winning columnists. Your new digital daily edition of The Independent gives you todays’ stories behind the headlines, with full global coverage of what is happening around the world and sections such as News, Culture, Lifestyle, Business, Tech and Sport.

Read our truly independent analysis on Brexit and the E.U., international politics, in-depth business and finance coverage, tech and lifestyle articles, free-thinking opinions and breaking stories from around the world. Follow our award-winning writers, including Robert Fisk on the Middle East and our top feature writers, including the acclaimed Simon Calder on Travel. You can also play interactive Crossword, Codeword and Sudoku puzzles each day on your device.

Features: 

News, Voices, Section 2, Obituaries, Business, Tech, Lifestyle, Sport, Crossword, Codeword, Sudoku. Additional stories and content from weekend supplements The New Review, Radar, Traveller and The Independent Magazine on Saturday and Sunday including Entertainment, Restaurants, Interiors, Gardening, Travel, Living, Cars and Property 

- Read the full range of The Independent’s content with simple navigation in an easy to use format

- Save stories and articles offline so that you can enjoy them later

- Browse award-winning journalism, enjoy concise informative content on Culture, Tech and Lifestyle

- Read comments on articles such as business and politics and share your own thoughts

- Comprehensive global sports coverage and updates on the latest football results

The latest digital edition automatically downloads each morning for you to stay up to date with today’s headlines and breaking news stories. The Independent Daily Edition presents a far more digital native reading experience for readers, the app is universal and tailored to whatever device you choose to read it upon. The app allows for font size changes, portrait or landscape orientation and plenty of other convenient user-friendly qualities.

The Independent Daily Edition offers you the latest breaking headlines and quality news commentary, informed opinions on global politics, Brexit and the E.U., business updates plus analysis, finance issues with detailed coverage of national and global headlines and incisive articles from an award winning team of journalists. Download the app today and start to discover the future of newspapers…

The app is FREE to download and can be read in one of the following ways: 

1) Weekly, Monthly and Annual subscriptions can be purchased and these subscriptions will auto-renew until you choose to cancel. 

2) Existing Independent app subscribers can use the app by validating their email address and password within the app. 

The weekly, monthly and annual subscriptions are auto-renewing subscriptions. Prices for the subscriptions are £2.99 for the seven day offering, £12.99 for one month and £149.99 for the annual subscription. Payment for this subscription will be charged to your Google Play account upon purchase. The subscription will auto-renew within 24 hours of the current subscription expiring. Auto-renewing subscriptions can be managed via Account Settings allowing them to be turned off. No cancellations of the current subscription are allowed during the active subscription period.

Privacy Policy: http://www.independent.co.uk/service/privacy-policy-a6184181.html
Terms of use: http://www.independent.co.uk/service/user-policies-a6184151.html

title: Touchtown Community Apps
description:
Everything you want to know about your senior living community is at your fingertips, anytime and anywhere, with Community Apps.

Here are just some of the features at your command with Touchtown:
• Activities — A complete, searchable community event schedule. Here residents can sign up for events, staff can easily manage registrations and details, prospects are wowed by distinct  offerings, and families feel confident in the services provided.
• Dining — Because aren’t we all wired to be curious about what’s for dinner? Take the guesswork out with a mouthwatering display of daily meal offerings. This is the MOST popular Apps module.
• Directories — An engaged community is an interconnected one. Empower community members to learn about each other, from next door neighbors to staff with searchable Resident and Staff Directories. In just a few taps, anyone can get in touch right from the app.
• Messages & Announcements — Everyone knows when yoga is cancelled. Loved ones show up for Family Day. Motivational messages are swiftly delivered to employees through push notifications. Prospects know when new apartments become available.
• Forms — Residents can easily submit requests, feedback and comments to staff. Staff can easily solicit, gather and review that input in a simple, streamlined manner. Maintenance requests, surveys, feedback and more — do it easily with Forms.

title: Connected Living Community
description:
Connected Living Community (CLC) is designed specifically for senior living residents, their families and friends. Users can connect directly to their communities to stay current with the most important information – calendars, dining menus, photos and more - and can utilize the private social feed to communicate with family and friends, share photos and enhance their quality of life.

CLC's most exciting feature - “Time Capsule” - allows users to capture their life stories in an easy-to-use, interactive format. Among other key features, you and your inner circle can easily use Connected Living for:

Accessing Community Information - Calendars, Menus, Photos, Alerts

Socializing - Private social networking capabilities with your inner circle of friends and family

Peace of Mind – Ability to share locations privately and get alerts when family or friends come and go from specific locations (i.e. “Mom’s place”)

Convenience: Access to features such as Lyft transportation, personal concierge services, personalized photo products, and more.

Connected Living Community includes a subscription upgrade that can provide some of our users access to two additional pieces of functionality.

1) Unlimited “Locations” – Our app lets users set up “Locations”. These Locations allow the user to receive alerts when their family and friends come and go from those locations. Free users have the ability to set up one location, while upgraded users can create unlimited locations.

2) The ability to access a 24/7/365 personal concierge - Users who choose to upgrade to the personal concierge gain access to that phone number within the app.

Subscription options are either $7.49 / month or $74.99 / Year.

Payment is charged to Google Play Account at confirmation of purchase.

Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period.

Accounts are charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period. Renewal cost dependent on the subscription selected ($7.49/month or $74.99/year).

Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase.

For more information on our privacy policy and terms and conditions visit http://connectedliving.com/privacy

Please note, continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.

title: Care of the Elderly
description:
Elderly care, or simply eldercare (also known in parts of the English speaking world as aged care), is the fulfillment of the special needs and requirements that are unique to senior citizens. This broad term encompasses such services as assisted living, adult day care, long term care, nursing homes (often referred to as residential care), hospice care, and home care. Because of the wide variety of elderly care found nationally, as well as differentiating cultural perspectives on elderly citizens, cannot be limited to any one practice. For example, many countries in Asia use government-established elderly care quite infrequently, preferring the traditional methods of being cared for by younger generations of family members.

Elderly care emphasizes the social and personal requirements of senior citizens who need some assistance with daily activities and health care, but who desire to age with dignity. It is an important distinction, in that the design of housing, services, activities, employee training and such should be truly customer-centered. It is also noteworthy that a large amount of global elderly care falls under the unpaid market sector.

The most important part of caring for the elderly is to love them and keep them active. There are many different ways to care for the elderly, whether by caring for them in the comfort of their own homes, bringing them to your home or moving them to a senior center.

title: Trusted Senior Care - health, wellness, safety
description:
In this modern world many elderly people live alone and families are spread out, living in different towns and countries. The app helps make it easier for families to care for a loved one – no matter where they are.

The app helps a family detect if a loved one is struggling. For example, it tells you if they are becoming forgetful or not maintaining their regular daily routines, such as remembering to take medicine. And it tells you if their physical activity is decreasing. It’s important to detect a decrease in physical activity because if they don’t receive some additional help then they could be at an increased risk of having a fall or suffer with reduced independence.

The app is technically advanced and features multiple built-in phone sensors. These sensors can give a family an advance warning that a loved one is struggling and lets you respond to ensure they receive the care they need.

A built-in motion sensor automatically lets the family know when (say) Grandmother moves or picks up her phone. In the morning it is reassuring to receive a message telling you your loved one has woken up at their regular time. And if you don’t get the message you know to call her and check everything is ok. 

The app lets you setup daily recurring reminders for your loved one, for example, at 10:00 every morning your Grandfather’s phone has a notification to (say) reminder him to take medicine. And you receive a message when they do it. It helps you to see if a person is maintaining their regular daily routines.  You can set this up from your phone – and select the reminders and tasks to appear on your loved ones phone. 

Mobile phones and tablets offer many benefits but for some older adults they struggle to use them as part of their daily lives. Perhaps they forget to charge the battery or they don’t keep it close by for when they need it (the phone is left untouched and forgotten).  The app helps a family to support a loved one to establish and maintain a daily routine of having a phone charged and close by. The app tells you if your loved ones phone battery gets low and it tells you when they charge their phone – so you can call and remind them if they forget to charge their phone.

The app is designed to help your elderly loved one with ‘everyday living’. The term ‘Everyday Living’ is incredibly important and encompasses:  (i) remaining socially engaged; (ii) continuing with activities that give life meaning; (iii) contributing to family or community; (iv) not feeling ‘burdensome’ to their families; and (v) continuing the role as caregiver.

The app links phones together to create a safe private group that helps people share, care and keeps people in touch.  The apps built-in sensors mean an elderly relative receives a continuous stream of family news feed events from their children and grandchildren.  

Please ask all your family to download the app and join your private group.

We hope you find the app useful. Please send us your feedback and suggestions on how to improve our app.

Lastly, please take a moment to rate this app if you find it beneficial.

title: Train your Brain - Visuospatial Games
description:
Visual skill games is an app that consists of several games to improve visual ability and train viso-spatial skills. Fun games for the whole family to keep the mind active in a playful way. This game is suitable for all ages, from the youngest to the elderly and senior players.

TYPES OF GAMES

- Repeat symmetrical patterns
- Locate an objective number within a numerical range
- Identification of 3D figures
- To stop moving elements
- Puzzles and shapes
- Estimation of perimeter and contour lengths.

Visual perception is the way we interpret and understand the information that is received through sight. With these games, the development of visoperceptive skills is stimulated in a playful and gamified way, performing tasks such as: Identify the relative position of objects, calculate distances, draw mental maps or mentally represent figures in three dimensions.

In the same way, these visual ability games help to recognize and distinguish sensory characteristics such as shape, color, depth, distance between objects, orientation or movement.

In addition to visuospatial processing, they also help to stimulate other areas such as attention or visual memory.

APP FEATURES

- Daily stimulation of visuospatial intelligence
- Available in 5 languages
- Simple and intuitive interface
- Different levels for all ages
- Constant updates with new games

GAMES FOR THE STIMULATION OF VISUAL-SPATIAL SKILLS

Visuospatial function is one of the essential cognitive functions in our daily life. The development of visuospatial abilities helps maintain a healthy mind and a healthy life.

Visuospatial processing is the ability to tell where objects are in space. It also helps to know how far objects are from others.

This collection of puzzles is developed in collaboration with doctors and experts in neuropsychology and is part of the collection of games for cognitive stimulation "Senior Games". In our developer profile you will find more games related to this project.


ABOUT TELLMEWOW

Tellmewow is a mobile games development company specialized in easy adaptation and basic usability which makes our games ideal for the elderly or young people who simply want to play an occasional game without major complications.

If you have any suggestions for improvement or want to stay informed about upcoming releases, follow us on our social networks.

@tellmewow

comments: These skills are challenging! That said, this is a great app with a good variety of co-ordination levels. Wish there was a daily challenge. Youbcan opt out of ads.

I was enjoying the app until I tried to play with the puzzle game. There is a problem with moving the pieces in to place. I could not get them to. move. It was like they were stuck to my screen. No matter; how hard I pushed, nothing moved. Most annoying; also as I got up to 7 and higher my scores went down and by accident I solved your problems. I turned my phone upside down and the pieces would move where I wanted them to go. My score should have been high and no negative reply.

Too many ads that play too long! This app is marketed for seniors, but some of the ads are not. Also, the app should have some "helps." I'm stuck on an upper level of a puzzle game and can't advance or do anything because I can't solve the puzzle. Ready to uninstall this app.

Every (often less than 30 seconds) a 30 second advertising clip even for the very first level does not give one the chance to give the game a reasonable try if it would be worth buying. (-2 stars) Make at least the first 4-5 levels of each game ad-free so people could test the app. Another star lost to directly sending the users to the app-store / installers, very bad for an app targeting also children. Last point: Am I lost, or is there nowhere an exit-button?

The games are challenging but who can be bothered when your screen is taken over by a long time after a very short time of play. Wordscapes should know that hell will freeze over before I'd download their app. Freeze just like they keep freezing my screen.Uninstalling , I don't recommend this one.

title: Train your brain - Coordination Games
description:
We present this collection of coordination games to develop and stimulate
the hand-eye movement ability. Fun coordination exercises for the whole family to stimulate the mind in a playful way. This game is suitable for all kinds of people, from the youngest to the elderly and senior players.

TYPES OF GAMES 

- Bimanual coordination of elements
- Selection of correct items
- Solve mazes using the gyroscope
- Decide between right and left side
- Avoid colliding with pieces
- Make series of numbers avoiding objects

In addition to coordination, these games help to stimulate other areas such as visual perception, psychomotor skills, attention or speed of processing.

APP FEATURES

- Fun daily brain training
- Available in 6 languages: Spanish, Italian, French, English, Portuguese and German.
- Easy and intuitive interface
- Different levels for all ages
- Constant updates with new games

GAMES TO STIMULATE COORDINATION

Coordination is one of the essential cognitive functions in our daily life. The development of coordination skills helps maintain a healthy mind and a healthy life.

Eye-hand coordination is the cognitive ability that allows us to perform tasks simultaneously using the eyes and hands. It is also defined as oculomotor coordination, oculo-manual, or visuomotor. These coordination games help to synchronize the action of the hand muscles to precise an appropriate speed and intensity of movement.

The different games of this app work different aspects of coordination such as accuracy, synchronization of both hands and fingers, fine motor, spatial orientation, the reaction speed or reflexes.

This app is a part of the collection of puzzles developed in collaboration with doctors and experts in neuropsychology for the cognitive stimulation of memory, attention, visuospatial function or reasoning, among others.

ABOUT TELLMEWOW

descriptionHTML:
We present this collection of coordination games to develop and stimulate
the hand-eye movement ability. Fun coordination exercises for the whole family to stimulate the mind in a playful way. This game is suitable for all kinds of people, from the youngest to the elderly and senior players.

TYPES OF GAMES

- Bimanual coordination of elements
- Selection of correct items
- Solve mazes using the gyroscope
- Decide between right and left side
- Avoid colliding with pieces
- Make series of numbers avoiding objects

In addition to coordination, these games help to stimulate other areas such as visual perception, psychomotor skills, attention or speed of processing.

APP FEATURES

- Fun daily brain training
- Available in 6 languages: Spanish, Italian, French, English, Portuguese and German.
- Easy and intuitive interface
- Different levels for all ages
- Constant updates with new games

GAMES TO STIMULATE COORDINATION

Coordination is one of the essential cognitive functions in our daily life. The development of coordination skills helps maintain a healthy mind and a healthy life.

Eye-hand coordination is the cognitive ability that allows us to perform tasks simultaneously using the eyes and hands. It is also defined as oculomotor coordination, oculo-manual, or visuomotor. These coordination games help to synchronize the action of the hand muscles to precise an appropriate speed and intensity of movement.

The different games of this app work different aspects of coordination such as accuracy, synchronization of both hands and fingers, fine motor, spatial orientation, the reaction speed or reflexes.

This app is a part of the collection of puzzles developed in collaboration with doctors and experts in neuropsychology for the cognitive stimulation of memory, attention, visuospatial function or reasoning, among others.

ABOUT TELLMEWOW

Tellmewow is a mobile game development company specialized in easy adaptation and basic usability which makes our games ideal for the elderly or young people who simply want to play an occasional games without major complications.

If you have any suggestions for improvement or want to stay tuned about upcoming games, follow us on our social networks.

@tellmewow

comments: Its ok. Its best for home window shopping. If you're seriously looking, it's less convenient. It assumes how much you're going to put down and what interest rate you've been approved for. There's no way to set those things so it gives you a more accurate idea of what you're paying each month. Plus, in my area theres a lot of 55+ communities and theres no way to filter those out, which is irritating.

I like this app, overall, but would really love to have the ability to hide or dismiss a property from my search, if it's not one that meets my needs. I like that I can save homes, but when searching later, homes keep popping up that I would rather not look at again! Also, if there is a way to get HOA/Space rent to be mandatory when there is one for the property, that would be great. I've looked at many that stated there was none, but that wasn't true. Thanks!

Zillow gave the option to turn off cookies, but did not bother to mention that it will erase all of your data when you do this. I went ahead and typed everything in once again, and it erased it AGAIN. Also, you can't add photos, videos, or tours with any Android phone -only i0s I want to know what kind of incentive apple is giving developers to leave these flaws in their designs..

I use this app almost daily, it keeps me up to date on homes that I am very interested in. We will be buying or building in the next 5 months, we are looking forward to building or buying our dream home. I love Zillow, I have found it to be more up to date than a Real Estate office. I highly recommend Zillow. Thank you, carolintallahassee

While the interface is the best I've seen out of all the other real estate options, the information is not accurate or up to date. If you try to get information from the listing agent on the app, a third party starts messaging you and sending your information to unrelated agents. I simply messaged asking about an open house and some random dude was trying to get me a new buyer's agent even though I already have one.

title: Senior Safety App, GPS Tracker, Fall Alerts & More
description:
Senior Safety App was designed to be installed on the Seniors smartphone. Caregivers get safety alerts with monitoring options via an online secure control panel. The app is popular with caregivers, concerned children of seniors and senior care homes too.

Monitor phone location & activity remotely over a web browser. Using a state-of-the-art GPS tracker, Senior Safety App helps you keep your elderly loved ones safe, with alerts for emergency help requests, malicious apps, phone falling, phone being inactive for a long time, app installs or uninstalls, entry/exit from geo-locations (buildings, streets, cities or neighborhoods), network changes (sim card change) and low battery alerts.

This app is to be installed on the Seniors phone. Caregivers use their email on the program and they can review alerts and reports via our online console at https://account.seniorsafetyapp.com

The app includes easy to use round-robin calling to reach one of the emergency contacts, this ensures help is received even if some emergency contacts may not answer their phone. This app was designed to help the elderly lead an independent life with their loved ones accessible at just a click of a button.


Simple. Easy. Powerful.

SOS & Alarm
Quickly request help when needed! SOS is easy to access option that is always available on the task list. Clicking this option sends out a text alert to multiple individuals, and each alert automatically includes the current device location. Single click option to call all emergency contacts one by one until the phone is answered. Powerful alarm function included for attracting attention during emergencies.

24/7 Senior GPS tracker
Monitor the seniors phone remotely from your dashboard to track current location and location history of up to 90 days. Keep an eye on your senior loved ones and ensure they travel safe, get their exercise and stay out of dangerous situations.

Fall Alert
If the phone user was to either has a fall or a sudden jerk while driving, the phone will send out a message to you. This settings sensitivity can be modified based on the phone user’s lifestyle.

Geo-fence Zone Alert
Receive alerts when the device leaves or enters a pre-configured geo-fence area, such as a neighborhood, a town or metropolitan area. Geo-fence alerts are sent out to your email with the current location of the device.

Inactivity Tracker
For seniors who live alone, this is a very important feature to let others know if they have been immobile for an extended amount of time. You can configure the time in hours based on the person's lifestyle. Receive alerts to your email.

Low Battery Alert
Phone is often the only contact with the outside world for many seniors, hence, keeping it charged is of utmost importance. Configure when you want to get alerts based on battery availability.

App Usage Report & Alerts
Review a list of apps that are in use on the phone with the time spent on each, receive an alert whenever a new app is installed or an existing app removed. Malicious apps have become commonplace with some that are specifically targetted to seniors.

Emergency Medical Information
Often details like doctors name, phone, medications, allergies, and other pertinent medical information remain unavailable during emergencies. Senior Safety App ensures all this and more is available at your fingertips if an emergency was to occur.

The Senior Safety App is popular with assisted living facilities, home healthcare companies and healthcare workers working with seniors across the world.

Read more at https://www.seniorsafetyapp.com

Email us your questions at support@seniorsafetyapp.com.

comments: I have been searching for an app like the Senior Safety App, one of the best apps. This app works very well. I can monitor where my grandpa is and come to know when his phone battery gets low and so many useful alerts. I highly recommended it!

I am so thankful that someone told me about Senior Safety App,, it has already help me , I have fallen several and it' works. I need to know how to fine tune the sensitive part, sometimes when I lay it on the bed it goes off. It's a real blessing to me. Thank you for creating this app Bob Miller

I have started using the Senior Safety App to monitor my father's movement. He is having the onset of dementia. So far, I find the app is quite helpful. I am monitoring the battery life of his cellphone, and I really liked the feature where I can add up to 5 emergency contact numbers; these numbers will be called one after another during an emergency. It really gives you peace of mind.

My grandmother has dementia. And the one thing that upsets her and causes panic attacks is loud noise. Dementia has made the effects of sensory changes like light and noise worse. Therefore, she gets anxious when her external environment gets too noisy. We tried everything. Finally, we found the Senior Safety App with its ability to alert us to fact that her surroundings are getting noisy before she panics. This app has helped me improve her quality of life.

My frail grandmother is 90 years old. Even though she stays in a nursing home, I installed the Senior Safety App on her phone to monitor her movements. If she falls and can’t get up, she presses the app’s SOS button. I phone the home and someone checks on her. The nursing home staff have been incredibly busy and stressed due to the lockdown. So, they appreciate the help. And I have peace of mind; my beloved grandmother is getting the best care possible.

Get all of our features, free to use, when you download our big and easy all-in-one home screen launcher for Android™!

TOP FEATURES
👍Large App Icons — Easy To See!

Specifically designed with seniors in mind, Big Keyboard Senior Home Screen is the easiest way to view all the important apps on your phone. We remove most of the clutter that makes a new phone difficult to learn and enlarge everything to make it easier to read and use.

Big Keyboard & Notifications - Senior Home Screen. Simple. Secure. Easy.

title: People Power Family
description:
The People Power Family app enables a first-of-its kind family care and connectivity product – the People Power Family Care Pack. The solution helps families address concerns of senior falls, wandering and loneliness in a new collaborative way. The solution uses machine learning algorithms to learn patterns of behavior and alert when dangerous events may be happening to dramatically lower costs of 24/7 senior care. The app connects to the People Power Family Care Pack which includes 1 Smart Home Center gateway that makes the system intelligent, 2 Entry Sensors to know when doors, medicine cabinets or refrigerators open and close, and 3 Motion Sensors to generate alerts of potential falls, wandering, and more. Installation is fast and simple. The Family Care Pack is available at PeoplePowerFamily.com

Optimized for families and senior care providers to help keep track of a senior and loved ones living alone or with a spouse or caregiver, the service can connect up to 10 people to conveniently share insights about a senior’s day-to-day wellness, and collaborate with a Trusted Circle™ of family and friends. The system distributes SMS text alerts about incidents that need immediate attention. If a situation requires an emergency response, anyone in the Trusted Circle who receives an alert can simply tap the phone number provided in the text message to facilitate direct phone contact with the Emergency Call Center. Help will be on the way.

Family Care Pack Benefits: 

•  Easily keep track of loved ones who may live alone, near or far away for enhanced peace of mind. •  Seniors can live at home longer delaying a costly move to an independent or assisted facility. •  Share good times and bad news with the Trusted Circle of family and friends. •  Control the system and collaborate naturally through simple text messaging – no app required for participants. •  If help is needed, the Trusted Circle and emergency services are notified. •  Expandable with today’s popular devices: voice control, smart plugs, water leak sensors, sirens, video cameras, lighting and more.

Android compatibility: - Devices shipped with (not upgraded to) Android OS v6.0.x or later - Chipset: ARMv7a or later

title: WIN: What I Need – Resources and Services
description:
WIN What I Need connects users to 12 categories of free resources.

WIN is free, easy to use, and empowers homeless, abused and resource-insecure youth, families and adults to find services that will help them build an independent life.

Users can search for anything, from food pantries and homeless shelters, to free health services, educational resources and more. More than a directory- WIN users can receive alerts about job fairs and other community events, offer feedback and connect to live assistance hotlines through the “I Need Help Now” page.

In addition to serving homeless, abused and struggling youth, families and adults, WIN (What I Need) is a powerful referral tool that anyone can use to guide others who need help or supportive services.

WIN is currently available in Los Angeles County, CA and Trenton/Mercer County New Jersey.

WITH WIN YOU CAN:

✔ Find job help, homeless shelters, free food pantries, healthcare, crisis support, drop-in centers, legal assistance, education resources, government benefits, public transportation, and more.
✔ Call domestic violence shelters, sex trafficking hotlines, mental health services, crisis and suicide prevention hotlines.
✔ Search for programs that serve your age, gender or region of the county.
✔ Find specialized resources just for veterans, LGBTQ, foster youth, pregnant and/or parenting teens or adults.
✔ View human services near you – they are listed first if your location is on.
✔ Use the map to see where a program is located.
✔ Read detailed information about each program to find the best “fit”

✔ Read or submit comments about user experiences.
✔ Call or email agencies using WIN app live links.
✔ Get directions to chosen agencies.
✔ View real time availability of beds at shelters.
✔ Share the app easily with others.
✔ Read or listen Helpful Info explanations about program or service options.
✔ Search even for services without an internet connection (although some features such as mapping, directions and real-time email are disabled).

Developer: OurChildrenLA
Contact: info@ourchildrenla.org
Copyright: OurChildrenLA 2019

title: India Flag Live Wallpaper
description:
A top quality Indian flag live wallpaper! A perfect live wallpaper for celebrating India Independence Day or Republic Day! Feel proud of your country? Let this Indian flag fly high in your phone!

APP HIGHLIGHTS
==============
✔ Real OpenGL 3D animation! Not a video loop or animated gif!
✔ Fully interactive! Shake phone, blow wind or touch screen to let the India flag fly!
✔ Play India national anthem!
✔ Floating cloud, thunderstorm, snowing, starry night etc animated background effect!
✔ Lighting control!
✔ Use own photo as background!
✔ Use own audio file as national anthem!
✔ Optimize for both tablet and phone, portrait and landscape mode!
✔ Set as live wallpaper or run as standalone app!

FLAG CONTROL
============
> Double tap to start/stop wind
> Double tap to start/stop background music

Feel proud of your country, let this India flag live wallpaper always flying high in your home screen!

title: Caremerge Family
description:
Caremerge Family Engagement is your one-stop shop to connect family members with their loved one’s senior care or other healthcare providers. We all live busy lives and this app helps us stay on top of our loved one’s care as it’s delivered in various care settings.

Key Features

- HIPAA-compliant messaging - no more phone tags to discuss medical updates or concerns, and no more delays in key decisions around care for your loved ones. Group messaging capability helps keep all authorized care providers and family members in the loop.
- Alerts and Notifications - stay on top of everything - receive alerts of new messages, real-time feed based on updates to care related activity performed for your loved one by the care providers (life enrichment activities, care provided during the day, etc.)
- Calendar and schedule - View the full range of activities and events being offered at the care provider setting (senior living, home health, day care, transitional care, etc.). Detailed event descriptions and dimensions of wellness icons provide insight into the purpose and value behind each activity and event.
- Care Locations - Make doctor’s visits and medication follow-up easy with integrated maps for preferred care locations and clickable phone numbers so you can get answers fast.

Good

Inconveniences: you have to login every time you use the app even though there's no sensitive data in it; you cannot save a location, even though there's a menu choice to show preferred locations; there's no help of any kind.

It will run in the background and notify you of activities that your family member participated in. But every time you see the notice you have to login with a complex password. When they allow fingerprint login or the option to stay logged in between reboots it will be an excellent app.

title: ZiffyHomes: Fully Furnished Studio Apartment/Flats
description:
ZiffyHomes is a "technology driven home rental marketplace" to make lives better by simplifying home rentals. We are a discovery platform which offers ready to move-in individual rooms in tastefully furnished flats to tenants for long stays. With ZiffyHomes, you don’t just rent a home but you rent a lifestyle! 

Ten noticeable features of ZiffyHomes are:

1. We provide brokerage free homes as there are no brokers involved. We have a team of dedicated sales specialist who help you find the right room, flat or apartment.
2. We provide individual rooms as a person’s freedom and independence is of utmost priority. Though we provide all the perks of co-living and a shared flat accommodation but we give due respect to an individual’s need for privacy.
3. We take care of all the documentation and legal processes like police verification and preparation of rent agreements so that our tenants do not have to spend time and energy on such statutory requirements.
4. We charge just 2 month’s rent as security deposit at the time of move – in. You do not have to worry about a huge chunk of your money being getting stuck. The move in process is smooth and handled professionally.
5. All our tenants are verified and niche working professionals, working with leading corporate and start ups of India. Thus, we are a network of like-minded individuals who prefer co-living over traditional PG. 
6. All our homes are tastefully furnished with contemporary furnishing for which we provide maintenance. We provide amenities like sofas, TV, internet and cable connection, washing machine, gas stove, oven, RO, double bed, mattresses, curtains, geyser, AC and host of other facilities. Thus, we work towards providing a standardized experience in all our homes. You can also customize the furnishings of your individual room to suit your taste.
7. We have a large network of ZiffyHomes across Gurgaon and Noida in niche localities with beautiful and safe surroundings. Thus, it is easy for you to find a ZiffyHomes near your office or close to the place of work or any other location of your preference in Gurgaon or Noida.
8. We provide online payments of monthly rent and other charges using all credit cards, debit cards, net banking and leading mobile wallet options. All the transactions are recorded and maintained to provide high levels of transparency.
9. We help you with the maintenance of your home. With ZiffyHomes you never have to worry about home maintenance errands as we run those for you. All you have to do is to notify our team and rest will be taken care of.
10. The move-out process is even smoother and you receive the refund within 7 working days after you evacuate the premises. We do not deduct money unnecessarily. 

How does our App make your life easier?

1. Search for an individual room, flat, apartment or house on the go. 
2. Search flats by localities, filtering them as per your need or based on areas on map view.
3. View the house details and real photographs with additional information like important places in neighbourhood and distances from landmarks.
4. You can either shortlist homes or schedule a visit as per a time of your convenience.
5. Once you have met your prospective roommates and you are sure of moving in a room of flat, you can book it from the app by making online payment. Say goodbye to cash woes.
6. You can upload the required documents on the app by taking their photographs by the app itself.
7. You can use the app to raise maintenance requests or notify us of any requirements. No more calls or emails to raise service requests.

So download the app to enjoy these features and much more!

House owners can get their properties listed. We furnish the property and find the right tenant for their house. The house owner get assured monthly rental without having to follow up for it while we maintain their property without converting it into a PG.

Visit: www.ziffyhomes.com
Write to us: support@ziffyhomes.com
Call us: 82 87 200 400

title: ShiftMed - Nursing Jobs
description:
ShiftMed empowers you to take control of your busy nursing work schedule. We instantly connect you with open shifts at local nursing homes, skilled nursing facilities, assisted living facilities, and hospitals. Finding medical work for you is our job, not yours!

How ShiftMed Works:

- Get Credentialed: You must have a CNA, LPN, or RN license in order to use the ShiftMed app. Once you have your nursing credentials in hand, we will manage and share them with our care providers to make sure you stay credentialed. 

- Claim Shifts: With our smart reminders, you’ll instantly be alerted when facilities post new shifts that fit your schedule. Work as little or as much as you want, and pick only the nursing shifts you want to work!

- Start Working: Every shift is an opportunity to learn something new. Meet other healthcare professionals nearby, travel to exciting new areas, and try out hospitals or nursing facilities! Positions include: CNA, LPN, GNA, and RN.

- Get Paid: Simply check-in and check out on the ShiftMed app, and facilities will approve your per diem hours. You work as an employee for ShiftMed when picking up shifts with us, not a contractor. Enjoy weekly pay, sick pay, and overtime as a caregiver.

It's never been easier to pick up per diem shifts in the medical staffing industry than with ShiftMed. Whether you’re looking for RN, LPN, or CNA shifts, you can rely on ShiftMed to give you the consistent jobs you dreamed of when you became a nurse.

title: Prey Day: Survive the Zombie Apocalypse
description:
In 2033, the world saw the outbreak of an unknown infection that left most of the human population dead.

Prey Day is an online, multiplayer, top-down shooter survival game which takes place in a huge city in a world after a zombie apocalypse. An unknown virus destroyed a large part of the population, leaving only the last handful of survivors on earth. Most of the inhabitants have become zombies or mutated under the influence of the virus. Among the labyrinth of empty streets, survivors fortify camps to resist zombie hordes, and venture outside to discover the cause of the infection that left the world in a state of survival.

You are one of the few survivors whose destiny is directly related to these events. In your life after the apocalypse, you'll deal with hunger and thirst, look for other survivors' camps, and spend your dark days crafting your own shelter from gathered materials. Investigate the causes of the infection that triggered the apocalypse by completing quests. Explore the darkest corners of the City to craft unique armor and weapons. Build vehicles that will grant you access to secret areas.

Confront other survivors, greedy for the loot you carry. Unite with others in the streets of Harbortown to fight back zombies and other survivors hiding and hunting for easy prey. Gather your friends and venture together into the most dangerous parts of the city.

HUGE ONLINE WORLD
The world of Prey Day is an open world shooting game set in a vast city destroyed by a wave of infection. You are left to survive with other humans - the real players. You can communicate with any player you meet, join them in a group, or fight against them to take their loot. There are no rules in open world games!

CLANS
Unite with other players in powerful clans, opening access to clan locations, where you can discover rare items and unlock new craft that can help you in the war against the undead. Together with your clan you can take over abandoned military bunkers, establish a clan base, and start real military action on the streets.

CRAFT
You can craft new weapons and equipment from various items collected on your journey. Trigger new craft recipes that can help protect your life against other players - crafting skills allow you to build your own shelter and protect it with traps!

ADVENTURE
What caused the apocalypse? In this zombie game you'll complete quests and explore Harbortown. The best zombie games have rich, mysterious storylines, and Prey Day is no different. Plunge into a whole series of adventures, going down into the city subway, traveling to the mountains and national parks on the edge of the city, and venturing through the wasteland, all while shooting your way through hordes of the walking dead.

RPG AND SURVIVAL
Prey Day is one of the most dangerous zombie survival games full of players who may have different goals and methods of survival - run, shoot, defend, team up, target, and fight real players fighting for survival just like you. Shooting games challenge your skill, speed, and reaction time, and when you're fighting for survival, you'll do everything you can not to die. With both co op and PVP elements, you can communicate and unite with friends, or oppose and kill competitors - the best traditions of MMO and online multiplayer games!

I would suggest lowering that a bit. Also getting a better backpack in the begining as well. Thank you hope to change rating soon.

Overall, it's OK. Good game, but with a few bugs that needs some tweaks. My problem is just that when I was on a pvp area, I got disconnected. When I logged back in, I LOST ALL MY STUFF. Game is slow to advance it's very difficult to get anywhere or generate resources .plus you lose all resource once your killed whic makes it even more impossible unless you purchase there packets which does you no good once you killed . So if you want to waist your time and repeat the same slow going process over and over with out spending a fortune just to lose everything you just purchased have at it. Oh and one more thing every enemy no mater what size or level is stronger than you ,faster

1 star, the New update destroyed the game. Instead of adding new multilayer and trading options they made the existing trading/pvp systems much worse. Also removed free options for farming to be replaced by new pay to play farming options. Peel back this update and create real multi-player options for your game or watch it die. Seriously like 30% of your players quit overnight. Idiots.

My last review of this game wasn't great but they need to fix the connection lost issues. The network connectivity in this game is the worst I have experienced so far. For a game with multiplayer features, it's connection issues is very bad and I have a fibre broadband at home and this issue still persist especially with watching ads for more loot which is good but if connecting afterwards takes over 20 seconds and the enemies can attack you while this is happening is just terrible. title: OurTime Dating for Singles 50+
description:
Our Time, Dating Made Easy

Our Time is the #1 dating app for mature men and women, with a simple mission: To help singles in their 50s, 60s, and beyond spark meaningful connections. Our unique focus is on celebrating this time of your life, and helping you find the quality connection you’re looking for. Whether it’s marriage, romance, friendship or companionship—we want to help you find that someone special to celebrate this time of your life with. In addition to being the best dating app for people over 50, we’re also safe and easy to use. We review every profile and every photo to help ensure the best quality of matches for you, and we’ve completely redesigned our App with the focus on simplicity. It’s easier to use and easier to personalize your profile for better match-making!

So join now, and find that connection you’ve been looking for! Go from wondering who’s out there to discovering someone wonderful.

We’re here to help you every step of the way. There’s no better time than now to go from wondering who’s out there to discovering someone wonderful. This is your time, so wait no more!

comments: The app along with their website is garbage. The matches are few and far between probably because the app and the website is garbage. Waste of money!!

I couldn't remember my password and they wanted me to enter the first 6 numbers and the last 4 of my credit card. If I do that just to reset my password, I might as well enter the entire 16 numbers. I blocked the card. I don't have to worry about renewal of the subscription. For what they offer, I come out better getting a man from under a bridge.

Wow did I screw up, this is a total waste of money. When I first signed up, they tried to charge my credit card a second time and thankfully my credit card company declined and and tagged as fraudulent. Extremely disappointed, DO NOT USE THIS APP!!

title: Home Security IP Camera: CCTV Surveillance Monitor
description:
Home Security Camera  🏠 is a smart system for guarding and monitoring your home. Simply connect any two devices and turn them into the perfect CCTV protection system. 

Do you feel nervous and uncomfortable when leaving your home unguarded? Home Security Surveillance app comes handy whenever you leave your house for work, vacation, or errands. In case of any suspicious activity, you can immediately inform the local authorities. 

The app and your phone create a powerful combination that serves the purpose well enough. Have your own security camera right in your pocket.

FEATURES:
»LIVE VIDEO MONITOR« 
- Home Security provides you with full-screen real-time video. 
- Streaming is the feature that keeps your house always guarded.
- Feel free to use the front or back camera of your monitoring device. 

»SAFE & RELIABILITY«
- The Home Security system works via WiFi, 3G, 4G or LTE networks. 
- It reconnects automatically and quickly in the case of WiFi outage! A wide range of supported networks brings you limitless connectivity.

»EASILY PORTABLE«
- Leave one device in the area you want to monitor and take the second device with you. 
- Home devices are easily portable, so you can check different angles and find the best spot for placing the surveillance security camera.

»USER-FRIENDLY«
- With the Home Security system, you can monitor your home with just one glance at your phone‘s display. 
- Appealing app design creates a unique user experience. 
- A wide range of settings gives you the power to control the areas as closely as you wish. 

»ALARM & NOTIFICATION«
- Home Monitor alerts you when the devices disconnect, or in case their battery drops below 10%. Rely on the accuracy of built-up alarms. 
- The app automatically creates a timeline of monitoring statuses, so you can view the whole history of sessions. 

»HIGH-QUALITY AUDIO SYSTEM« 
- You can hear every tiny noise or sigh of sound in a live audio-video stream. 
- Use the Home Security monitor app as an audio remote control of your safe home. 
- Set up the noise sensitivity, which will determine when the app notifies you that there is something going on in the monitored area. 
- You can use the monitoring device as a walkie-talkie by pressing the mike button. 

»MULTIPLATFORM SECURITY CAMERA«
- The Home Security System can monitor up to 4 independent areas. 
- The number of Home Security Cameras units is limitless! 
- You can even connect to devices on different software platforms.
- Create areas, name them and begin to watch the scenes on your screen.

»FAST CONFIGURATION«
- Fast and secure configuration over local WiFi with automatic device lookup or over QR invitation code takes less than 30 seconds. 

»SECURITY FIRST«
- All communication between the CCTV devices is securely encrypted via private cloud solution. 
- Industry-standard encryption is used to ensure that only your viewers have access to your stream.

title: Best Studio Apartment Plan Design
description:
If you are looking for ideas to decorate a small studio apartment you need to think about the type of furniture that is suitable and the amount of colour that you introduce into the space. These could have a positive effect on your living experience if they are looked at properly. 

Apartments for rent 
As compared to purchasing a home, apartments for rent is always one of the best options and easy. So the moment you rent any apartment you certainly can enjoy a number of benefits.

Houses for rent 
A house for rent by owner is a business, and you have to manage it like any other business. Determine the rent and know how much to charge for rent. Charge too little and you lose money, and if you exceed the standard rate, your house remains vacant.

Studios for rent 
Apartments for Rent are certainly one of the most opted for these days. With each passing year, more and more people are opting to rent apartment opposed to buying a house.

One bedroom apartments 
One-bedroom apartments give individuals and couples more space than most studios, without the sometimes non-standard design of a larger two-bedroom. Traditional rental units are defined as a one-bedroom when there is a separate bathroom and a separate bedroom connected to a central living area.

title: Pakistan independence Day  - 14 August 1947
description:
Pakistan Independence Day 2019 which is celebrated on 14 august (Pakistan Day) app is an online app which includes everything whatever is needed like, Video Status, Image Status, Text Status, Wallpaper, Poetry and Songs. The best part of this app is, it is updated regularly. It has unlimited collection of these thing. We have made sure that nothing stops you from your enjoyment, you do not need to search on internet as everything is available in this app.

Pakistan Independence Day 2019 (14 august) app allows you to download and share everything with your friends and family. So, you can wish Azadi Mubarak easily through our application. Best and great collection of mili naghmay. National songs of Pakistan.

Jashan e Azadi Songs and Azadi Mubarak Wishes can be shared through this application. Azadi Video Status can also be seen and shared with family and friends.

Pakistan has got its freedom in 1947 14 august. People celebrate jashan e azadi by listening and dancing to azadi songs and greet with azadi mubarak.

Happy Independence Day To You All!
Pakistan Zindabad

About...

Independence Day (Urdu: یوم آزادی‎; Yaum-e Āzādī), observed annually on 14 August, is a national holiday in Pakistan. It commemorates the day when Pakistan achieved independence and was declared a sovereign state following the end of the British Raj in 1947. Pakistan came into existence as a result of the Pakistan Movement, which aimed for the creation of an independent Muslim state in the north-western regions of South Asia via partition. The movement was led by the All-India Muslim League under the leadership of Muhammad Ali Jinnah. The event was brought forth by the Indian Independence Act 1947 under which the British Raj gave independence to the Dominion of Pakistan which comprised West Pakistan (present-day Pakistan) and East Pakistan (now Bangladesh). In the Islamic calendar, the day of independence coincided with Ramadan 27, the eve of which, being Laylat al-Qadr, is regarded as sacred by Muslims.

The main Independence Day ceremony takes place in Islamabad, where the national flag is hoisted at the Presidential and Parliament buildings. It is followed by the national anthem and live televised speeches by leaders. Usual celebratory events and festivities for the day include flag-raising ceremonies, parades, cultural events, and the playing of patriotic songs. A number of award ceremonies are often held on this day, and Pakistanis hoist the national flag atop their homes or display it prominently on their vehicles and attire.


In 1946, the Labour government in Britain, exhausted by recent events such as World War II and numerous riots, realized that it had neither the mandate at home, the support internationally, nor the reliability of the British Indian Army for continuing to control an increasingly restless British India.

Happy Independence Day To You All!
Pakistan Zindabad

About...

Independence Day (Urdu: یوم آزادی‎; Yaum-e Āzādī), observed annually on 14 August, is a national holiday in Pakistan. It commemorates the day when Pakistan achieved independence and was declared a sovereign state following the end of the British Raj in 1947. Pakistan came into existence as a result of the Pakistan Movement, which aimed for the creation of an independent Muslim state in the north-western regions of South Asia via partition. The movement was led by the All-India Muslim League under the leadership of Muhammad Ali Jinnah. The event was brought forth by the Indian Independence Act 1947 under which the British Raj gave independence to the Dominion of Pakistan which comprised West Pakistan (present-day Pakistan) and East Pakistan (now Bangladesh). In the Islamic calendar, the day of independence coincided with Ramadan 27, the eve of which, being Laylat al-Qadr, is regarded as sacred by Muslims.

The main Independence Day ceremony takes place in Islamabad, where the national flag is hoisted at the Presidential and Parliament buildings. It is followed by the national anthem and live televised speeches by leaders. Usual celebratory events and festivities for the day include flag-raising ceremonies, parades, cultural events, and the playing of patriotic songs. A number of award ceremonies are often held on this day, and Pakistanis hoist the national flag atop their homes or display it prominently on their vehicles and attire.


In 1946, the Labour government in Britain, exhausted by recent events such as World War II and numerous riots, realized that it had neither the mandate at home, the support internationally, nor the reliability of the British Indian Army for continuing to control an increasingly restless British India.

title: QuickBooks Self-Employed:Mileage Tracker and Taxes
description:
Are you self-employed, a freelancer or an independent contractor? Organize your finances with QuickBooks Self-Employed and let us help you find your tax deductions & maximize tax returns in time for tax season!. Put more money in your pocket during IRS tax season with this convenient mile tracker, expense tracker, invoice generator and tax deductions estimator. Become a tax pro - send invoices online with easy-to-use online services. 

QuickBooks Self-Employed users have found billions in potential tax deductions by automatically tracking mileage for work, tracking business expenses and sending invoices online. Save receipts and attach them to business expenses, send  invoices and categorize business expenses apart from your personal finances. Get all the tax refunds a self-employed business owner is entitled to! 

Track Mileage Automatically!.
•  Mileage tracking automatically works using your phone’s GPS, without draining your phone’s battery.
• Trip mileage is saved and categorized to maximize mileage tax deductions.

Scan Receipts
• Receipt scanner enters transaction information & can easily save receipts - making tracking business expenses much easier.
• Business expenses are automatically matched and categorized – saving you time and maximizing your tax refunds so that you are ready for IRS tax time.

Expense Tracker to Organize Business Expenses
• Self -employed, freelancer or small business owner – manage business finances easily and keep up to date so you do not miss out on any tax deductions.  
• Import business expenses directly from your bank account.

Get Paid Faster
• Create invoices and send invoices easily on the go. 
• Enable payments and bank transfer services to get paid faster.
• Invoice generator – get notified when invoices are sent, paid, and money is deposited!

Stay Prepared For Tax Time
• We take care of your bookkeeping so you can avoid year-end surprises 
• Easily organize income and business expenses for instant tax filing
• Directly export Schedule C income and expenses.
• Instantly export your financial data to TurboTax Self-Employed by upgrading to the Tax bundle*.

*Users will receive one state and one federal tax return filing.

title: LeapFrog Academy™ Educational Games & Activities
description:
Go on a learning adventure and subscribe to receive 2,000+ Learning Activities with No Ads

Help your child build core developmental and cognitive learning skills through interactive modules and games. 

LeapFrog Academy is an educational app designed by educators and built by the leading brand in kids learning to assist 3, 4, 5, and 6-year-olds in their development and independent education. 

Through our features and learning programs, your child will be taught:
• Reading & Writing: Become confident readers with lessons in the ABCs, syllables, letters, and rhymes.
• Math: Count, compare, and sort to think critically and solve problems. 
• Science: Advance STEM skills and explore life cycles, the human body, and additional observations.
• Critical Thinking: Exercise logic and reasoning. 
• Creativity in a Blend of Art & Music: Learn to create and inspire. 
• Social & Emotional skills to benefit health and feelings. 

Our subscription platform is one of the best learning apps for kids to learn traditional school subjects like reading, writing, and math, blended with life skills like problem solving and critical thinking.

Subscription Details:
Upon downloading the app, choose your subscription plan and activate a 30-day free trial. Cancel any time from your Google Play account and enjoy the app until your subscription plan ends.
• While the app is free to download, one of three subscription plans is required to access the program. Choose from the following plans to get started:
• Monthly Plan: $7.99/month
• 6-Month Plan: $39.99 every 6 months
• 12-Month Plan: $69.99 every 12 months
• FREE 30-day trial starts after you sign up for the subscription
• Subscription fee will be charged on the first day following the 30-day free trial and will be charged to your Google Play account
• Subscription is automatically renewed at the end of each billing period unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current billing period
• Subscription can be managed at any time via your Google Play account
• If you have any questions, visit www.leapfrog.com/support

The program includes more than 2,000 of our best eBooks, games, puzzles, and videos. Track progress within My Learning Lab, earn rewards, and unlock new interactive lessons as you complete an activity.

The Parent Dashboard lets you choose and change your kid’s Learning Adventure and see what activities are offered in My Learning Lab. It also lets you see how your child is progressing, view your account, manage each profile, and more.

Enjoy all the benefits of the best education app for kids without an internet connection by adding up to 24 lessons and activities to your Favorites. 

LeapFrog Academy™ learning app is a safe environment for children. There is no advertising or ability for an external party to contact your child.

Help your child build a strong educational foundation with this well-rounded curriculum.

Terms and Conditions: www.leapfrog.com/terms-academy
Privacy Policy: www.leapfrog.com/privacypolicy

comments: Giving it a 3 star because the newest update totally changed the look of the app and its awful. It works, it's fine, if you download it now you may like it not having seen it as before. But as someone thats been using this app for years...two thumbs way way down on the updated look. Its not easy on the eyes, the ads on the bottom are a wicked turn off, just overall disappointed. Wish I didn't update it.

Used to be really good because it was simple. Now the minimalist design was replaced with 2 new features that have no tutorial or detailed explanation on how to properly use. Here's the problem, there's too much inputting and figuring out. Blocks vs Routines vs Programmer? I preferred simply making different weeks, copying them and slightly alternating them if anything pops up.

Really enjoyed this app, but was disappointed to find it doesn't automatically sync your schedule to your account. I had to reset my phone and was bummed to see the schedule, routines, and tags I worked on for days, tweaking it to fit my kid's days perfectly was gone. Not sure I will take the time to redo it and will probably not use the app anymore although I really did like it. If you do use it, just make sure you back up your schedule!!

It's fairly good. I'm mainly posting this review to suggest that timetune pro be a monthly subscription of a dollar. Some people might not go for that but in reality it would help the developers to be better funded so they could make the app the best of its kind. Is timetune the best? no. Its potential is incredible though and I really like the approach and Design.

Hi TimeTune, I love your app since then. I just have a problem. I don't know how to fix the blockage of TimeTune app on my Infinix Hot 9. Your site for troubleshooting is not accessible for me. Overall this app is fine and satisfying. Edit. Troubleshooting doesn't work on Infinix Hot 9. Hoping for its inclusion on troubleshooting sites. Edit. I can't find any forums. I am hoping for more improvements in the future. I'll be reinstalling the app after the update.

title: ServerLife - Tip Tracker
description:
ServerLife is the best Tip Tracker app that enables you to clearly see the money you earn.

275,000 people like you have entered over 15 Million tips!

Are you tired of never knowing exactly how much money you make because it ends up as cash in your pocket? ServerLife solves that.

ServerLife is perfect for anyone whose income is variable and fluctuates from week to week.

Hospitality Industry (Servers, Bartenders, Hosts)
Uber & Lyft Drivers
Shoppers (Shipt, Instacart)
Hair Stylist, Barbers, Makeup Artists
Fitness and Yoga Instructors, Personal Trainers
Real Estate Agents
Sales (Commission based)
Freelancers & Entrepreneurs
Small Business Owners
Self Employed Individuals
Postmates Couriers
Independent Contractors

Enter your earnings at the end of your shift and easily see your totals. You'll be able to clearly see which days pay the best with our powerful filtering and comparison logic. 

You can easily track the following values for each entry:
- Tips
- Hours
- Notes

HISTORY
The History page will show you the total tips and wages you earned for the any week, 2 weeks, semimonthly, month and year. 

DAILY AVERAGES
Want to see the daily average for any month and year - head over to the Averages page. This page breaks down the daily averages for any month and the entire year.

REMINDERS
You can configure ServerLife to remind you to enter your tips. We all get busy and forget important things sometimes. Have ServerLife remind you to enter your tips at the same time every day.

START OF WEEK
Does your pay week start on a Tuesday? No problem you can change the start of the week so that the charts and totals will align with how you get paid. 

NEXT LEVEL
Want even more from the app? Take your tracking to the next level with the in app purchase of the Advanced features. With the in app purchase you'll be able to see:

- Work Schedule
- Credit/Cash Tips
- Expenses
- Sales Total/Tip %
- Pictures
- Hourly Wage
- Covers
- Tips/Sales per Cover
- Miles/Deliveries
- Mile and Delivery Fee
- Tip Out (Tips to others)
- Tip In (Tips to you)
- Weekly and Monthly Averages

WORK SCHEDULE
Tired of always referring back to the picture you took of the schedule? Quickly enter your weekly schedule and add default reminders so you're never late again.

EXPENSES
Have additional expenses that you payout to work, i.e. childcare, meals at work, transportation, or Tip Out multiple positions? Track them with Expense categories.

HOURLY WAGE
Want to include your hourly wage with your tips? Track your hourly wages so that your earnings are more accurate.

GOALS
Studies have shown that when you set a goal for yourself you are more likely to progress faster towards that goal. You can set daily, weekly, and monthly goals with any of the 17 fields the app calculates.

TRACK MULTIPLE JOBS
Work multiple Jobs or different Positions that have a different hourly wage? You can track the following with the in app purchase:
- Multiple Jobs, Positions (with different hourly wage), Sections, and Shifts (save the typical start and end time and it'll populate when you enter your tip)

COMPARE
Compare all of these on the Compare page. Here you can compare your Jobs, Positions, Sections, or Shifts to see which one you're making the most money.

FILTER
Once you start tracking your Jobs, Positions, Sections or Shifts you can filter any of the pages to show any combination of these. You can also filter to show Paychecks or Tips.

IMPORT YOUR DATA
Upgrading from the Just the Tips or TipSee app? Email us your latest backup file and we'll import it for you. Step by step instructions are located on the Import button on the Settings page.

SAFE AND SECURE
Your data is always safe and secure. You never have to worry about backup files or when was the last time the data synced with the cloud. All of your data is saved to our private cloud securely every time you make a change. It is available on all of your devices. Even if you lose and get a new phone your data will always be safe.
