- Hourly Wage
- Covers
- Tips/Sales per Cover
- Miles/Deliveries
- Mile and Delivery Fee
- Tip Out (Tips to others)
- Tip In (Tips to you)
- Weekly and Monthly Averages

WORK SCHEDULE
Tired of always referring back to the picture you took of the schedule? Quickly enter your weekly schedule and add default reminders so you're never late again.

EXPENSES
Have additional expenses that you payout to work, i.e. childcare, meals at work, transportation, or Tip Out multiple positions? Track them with Expense categories.

HOURLY WAGE
Want to include your hourly wage with your tips? Track your hourly wages so that your earnings are more accurate.

GOALS
Studies have shown that when you set a goal for yourself you are more likely to progress faster towards that goal. You can set daily, weekly, and monthly goals with any of the 17 fields the app calculates.

TRACK MULTIPLE JOBS
Work multiple Jobs or different Positions that have a different hourly wage? You can track the following with the in app purchase:
- Multiple Jobs, Positions (with different hourly wage), Sections, and Shifts (save the typical start and end time and it'll populate when you enter your tip)

COMPARE
Compare all of these on the Compare page. Here you can compare your Jobs, Positions, Sections, or Shifts to see which one you're making the most money.

FILTER
Once you start tracking your Jobs, Positions, Sections or Shifts you can filter any of the pages to show any combination of these. You can also filter to show Paychecks or Tips.

IMPORT YOUR DATA
Upgrading from the Just the Tips or TipSee app? Email us your latest backup file and we'll import it for you. Step by step instructions are located on the Import button on the Settings page.

SAFE AND SECURE
Your data is always safe and secure. You never have to worry about backup files or when was the last time the data synced with the cloud. All of your data is saved to our private cloud securely every time you make a change. It is available on all of your devices. Even if you lose and get a new phone your data will always be safe.
summary: Start tracking your income!
recentChanges:
Added new date ranges to the charts including Week, Pay, Month, Year and Custom. You can also compare time periods now. See the increase or decrease between time frames to see if you're doing better.

Added a new To Date chart which shows you your cumulative totals over a given period.

If you love the app please leave a review, or if you have a suggestion or issue contact me from the Chat with Support on the More tab or from www.serverlifeapp.com
comments: Been looking for an app that does it all for a server and i found it, A+.

I used to have a 5* review. I installed this app on every device I owned. It was simple, and easy to use. Now days, the ads are obtrusive. There is a subscription fee to remove ads. It is not a one time fee, but a recurring fee. This basically ruins the app. The only reason i have 2* is the developer helped me with some data issues i had a few years ago, and i still appreciate that. I would pay a one time fee to remove ads forever, because i like the simple functionality, but now...uninstall.

Great app that's very easy to use. Wonderful customer service. I appreciate that he responded so quickly and took the extra effort to dig deeper into the problem and collaborate in in order to find a solution if possible. Exceptional Service.

I use this everyday I work. Super organized and easy to use. Also, when covid shut down everything, the app had information about it and also notified me that there was a grant I could apply for specifically for servers that got me $500 extra.

title: TYT - Home of Progressives
description:
The TYT app features top-rated shows from the largest progressive news and talk network for the connected generation, including The Young Turks, The Damage Report, NoFilter, and The Conversation. Tune in live or on-demand to watch hosts Cenk Uygur, Ana Kasparian, John Iadarola, along with our many other hosts, as they discuss news and politics with no holding back.

Getting started is easy. Just download the app and enjoy our free videos, podcasts and live streams. Some of our programs are marked for TYT Members only with a "Plus" banner - if you want to watch or listen to those programs, membership starts at $4.99 a month.  Watch and listen on your phone or at www.TYT.com. Cancel anytime.

A paid membership to TYT includes:
- Access to all videos and podcasts: members get full-size versions of all shows and podcasts, with more than 15 hours of live content per week. 
- Get the news you care about:  Customize your notifications to receive updates on live shows, special events, and breaking news.
- Support independent journalism: TYT covers stories that fall through the cracks and are ignored by major media organizations.
- Hold the establishment accountable: We take politicians on both sides of the aisle to task for their actions every day.

Payment is charged to the Google Play Store account at confirmation of purchase. Your account will be automatically charged each month for renewal at least 24 hours before the end of the current billing period.  You can manage your subscription and auto-renewal by visiting your Google Play Store Account Settings.  If you turn off auto-renew during the current subscription period, your subscription will be canceled for the subsequent period.  

For help, please visit https://accounts.TYT.com/FAQ

title: The Epoch Times: Live & Breaking News
description:
The Epoch Times App serves you with trusted news wherever you are. Get instant access to award-winning journalism, breaking, political, US, China, and world news, as well as news on arts and culture, and more.

With The Epoch Times App you can browse our digital content, including in-depth coverage of China, unbiased reporting on US politics and the 2020 election.
You will also get access to our premium shows such as Declassified, American Thoughts Leaders,  Crossroads, The China Report, China Uncensored, Zooming In as well as commentaries and documentaries on issues that matter. 

Download the  app to experience our digital publishing platform. 

MAIN APP FEATURES:

• Top section: See important events and hot topics in the US, China and around the world at a glance.
• Breaking news alerts: Get the latest news in a timely manner as they happen.
• Livestream notification:  Watch live broadcasts of major events in the US and around the world.
• Video section: Enjoy exclusive, original series, inspiring videos as well as documentaries.
• Opinion: Read political, social, and personal commentaries. 
• Save articles into your personalized reading list.
• Share content easily on all major social media platforms such as Twitter and Facebook as well as via email or text message.
• Adjust font size in articles. 


Terms of service: https://www.theepochtimes.com/terms-of-service

We are working hard to ensure our readers have an excellent experience using our app! If you have any questions about how the app works, want to provide us with insightful feedback, or experience any technical difficulties such as crashes, please contact us at app@epochtimes.nyc. This way our developers can identify and resolve issues in a timely manner.

comments: One of the best news source bar none. Multiple choices for different areas of interest and special and breaking news and world events. They even have an entertainment and game section. Too much to mention. They provide the facts and they have real, not fake news and an opinion section with seasoned reporters. The video section and news channels will make you glad you took a solid step into the light and out of the darkness of the legacy media. Highest recommendation.

Great app, up-to-date news with excellent research and reporting involved, especially as it concerns China, which had otherwise kicked out or sent money to most major networks. I would have given it less stars, as I don't like the subscription price ($5 a month or no fee and some ads would be better) but I don't read many more than the few 'free articles' advertised as the option for non-subscribers.

My my favorite news source! real news. In a world filled with fake news the Epoch Times stands out. The Epoch Times has held on to the original spirit of the news, sharing the facts with the people. They go after the stories the corrupt mainstream media and turned a blind eye to as it does not fit their agenda. The Epoch Times does not do this. Prepare for a breath of fresh air as you read some real news by real journalists about real events happening in our world. Thank you Epoch Times.

Was a great app! I was really enjoying it till the sneaky upgrade now limits you and now has ads AND forces you to subscribe! $77 special rate and then $192 /yr??? ...for an app??? You lost me. I will be deleting like many others. No thanks!

my very favorite source of news. Easy to scroll down through the stories and click on the one I'm interested in. I love that I can scroll down through a story and find a video click on along with the names I need to go on YouTube for the research. I prefer to listen to the actual people rather than having people tell me what they think that person said and the epoch times has been my best source of obtaining the names behind the story.

title: Virtual High School Girl family Iove simulator
description:
Celebrate independence day as a high school girl spectate pak army troops parade


Independence day 14 august 1947 is the republic day festival when our beloved country Pakistan came into being the historic day when we got freedom from British government and the day on which the most powerful country appears on the map of the world in the name of Islam so that Muslims of sub-continent live their life according to the teaching of Islam. Everyone celebrate this independent day with great joy this game is also based on the girl story that celebrate our national day by participating in various events the whole schedule of a day for a school girl is virtually presented to the user in which user play the role of a girl and celebrate the historic day that differentiate it from other independence day games, high school games, pak army games or high school simulator that are based on the school life.
First the high school girl has to attend the ceremony of independence day that held in the school different challenging tasks related to the game need to be completed such as reach the school at time, decorate the school with other high school student, participate in flag ceremony, sing the national songs, spectate the whole 14 august ceremony perform the speech and many more interesting tasks are at your disposal just like school sim. This is the initial stage of the game after the Independence Day event in school the next stage in the game is to celebrate the Independence Day with your parents. Learn the history from grandparents listen to the speech of prime minister of Pakistan and learn use full information about Pakistan history and the efforts behind it.

Finally you as a girl visit the , wagha border ceremony to celebrate the final moments you take part in flag hoisting ceremony at border raise the spirit of soldiers spectate the performance of pak army bands, army march,  Pak army parade and  many other challenging missions related to different events occurring at the independent day need to be completed by you as a girl as well as you went out with your friends participate in rally’s spectate amazing jf 17 thunder jets, f16 and other fighter jets fly pass and show your patriotism and sincerity with country and  Many other side quests include decorating the streets raising the flags on this flag day on the houses decorating the houses and many other tasks that player can explore while wandering around the city  Player can buy various items such as flags , shirts , gadgets and other various items as the game proceeds so happy independence day from all of us and start playing this game as true patriot.

Features
•	High definition graphics with realistic environment
•	Multiple missions related to 14 august
•	Celebrate 14 august with real life experience
•	Take part in Pakistan flag ceremony
•	Fabulous 3d real life game play with attractive sounds and smooth controls

title: Moonlighting: Freelancer Jobs, Tools & Benefits
description:
Moonlighting is designed to take the hassle out of your hustle. 

Whether you’re a freelancer, gig-worker, contractor, part-timer or side hustler, as a Moonlighting member you can access a full suite of powerful business management tools, commission-free jobs, discounts and benefits for the modern worker.

As Featured In: FastCompany, Entrepreneur, Inc., Forbes, Huffington Post, Buzzfeed & more.

Our mission is to provide you with the tools that make it easy for you to focus on making money and building your financial independence. How do we do that?

We make attracting new clients and finding work less costly and time-consuming
• Get noticed by listing the services you provide and easily building a web page that showcases your expertise, experience, certifications, and reviews.
• We are constantly adding new jobs that are curated for independent workers and are available with no commission or bidding fees.

We understand chasing down payments is the worst
• Create professional proposals and invoices with integrated payments to secure a steady cash flow. 
• Securely accept payments anytime, anywhere via credit card, ACH, and PayPal with no hidden fees.

We know finding work and getting paid is just half the adventure
• NEW!! Access essential benefits that help you grow and protect your business and personal life. Whether you want to save money setting up an LLC, earn a little extra cash in your new bank account or access educational courses to up your skills, we’ve got you covered.

We always keep you up to date
• Moonlighting will alert you anytime a relevant job is posted, a client reaches out, a proposal is accepted, or a payment is received, so that you’ll always know where your business stands.

title: Independence Day Wallpapers
description:
🎇 Are you a proud American, looking for a collection of wallpapers with patriotic motifs to decorate your screen with? No worries, Independence Day Wallpapers are a new collection of free “USA flag backgrounds” and symbols of freedom which will show your true devotion to the red, white and blue! Salute the flag, gaze at the stars and stripes and show everyone that you are a true American with these amazing freedom wallpapers and backgrounds! Celebrate the upcoming freedom festival with “4th of July” pictures, images of the star-spangled banner, a beautiful “fireworks wallpaper” and much more! Your screen will shine with pride the second you download this “fireworks live wallpaper” and set the “independence day backgrounds” as your default home and lock screen images! Download this collection of “free live wallpapers for Android™” and have a very “happy 4th of July”!

- Long press on the home screen until the menu labeled “set wallpaper” comes out, choose the category “live wallpapers” and scroll to “Independence Day Wallpapers”.

title: MyHeritage - Family tree, DNA & ancestry search
description:
Build your family tree on the go - MyHeritage genealogy puts your family history right at your fingertips.

Explore your roots, find new relatives, and make amazing discoveries. Join our global community of users and build your family tree -- it’s easy and intuitive.

Build Your Family Tree

Add your parents, grandparents, and other relatives to grow your family tree on the MyHeritage app. Discover and treasure your ancestors’ stories by building a family tree you’ll want to share and preserve for generations to come.

Research your family history with MyHeritage’s award-winning products, all private and secure. Sync between them and enjoy a captivating journey to your past, wherever you are.

Make Instant Family History Discoveries

title: Harvest Hosts - Unique RV Camping Experiences
description:
Are you looking for new opportunities to explore and enjoy the RVing lifestyle?

Harvest Hosts offers unique RV camping at 1300+ wineries, breweries, farms, museums, golf courses and unique attractions that invite RVers to visit and stay overnight for free.

Instead of a box store parking lot, make memories with a unique RV experience! Our membership is a special opportunity to meet amazing entrepreneurs, enjoy delicious wine tastings, peek inside working farms, and behold awesome museum exhibits.

To participate, you need a qualified self-contained RV, as Host locations do not provide any hookups or services such as bathrooms. No tent-trailers, outdoor kitchens or tents of any kind are allowed.

Harvest Hosts encourages all RV Members to support local economies by making purchases from their Hosts to thank them for their hospitality. When considering how much to spend at a Host location, please be generous and keep in mind your campground fee savings. Most of these purchases will be things you probably already buy; produce at the farm, wine at the vineyard, and entrance to a unique attraction.

comments: Can't be beat! The app is easy to use when traveling. We have stayed at 15-20 Harvest Hosts and all have been great experiences true to the app. Some have been spectacular and I have even used them for buying unique gifts for friends!

5 stars became 2... Really enjoyed my experience until my credit card was charged for another year and I dont want it, I'm not traveling. Add to that a lack of Canadian spots, lack of contact information and my level of frustration!

I like it. Best part is that there is so much variety in the hosts and that makes it fun for us. I wish navigating the map was easier (that the icons were smaller when zoomed out), but not a huge deal.
Have loved all the HH locations we've stayed with! During Covid19 restrictions some offer less, but everyone has been so welcoming. App is easy to use & very instructive. Don't change a thing!

Update: cancelled membership. App KILLS data. Not recommended. ********** Buggy app. Buttons randomly won't work. How the program works: 1. Pay an annual fee for details (Host name, contact number, company website, specific address) 2. Call Hosts directly to see if they have any openings and to reserve a site 3. Arrive during business hours 4. Buy something from Host. It's a great marketing opportunity for Hosts. Note, your unit must be self-contained; Hosts do not provide any hookups.

title: uLesson - Your Learning App
description:
Learn better, get higher grades.

uLesson, the largest and fastest-growing learning platform in West Africa, is designed with the purpose of helping students like you improve and excel in your academics, including class tests and exams, JSCE,  BECE, WASSCE & SSCE.

The uLesson app offers comprehensive learning programs in Mathematics, Integrated Science, Basic Design and Technology, and Business Studies for Junior secondary school students, and Mathematics, Physics, Chemistry, and Biology for Senior secondary school students.

On the uLesson App, you can attend Live Lessons by Top Tutors covering subjects from JSS1 - SSS3, revise and relearn topics through engaging pre-recorded video lessons, perfect your understanding through practice questions and quizzes with detailed solutions, and prepare for exams through several years of WAEC past questions with solutions.

Please note that for an optimal experience on uLesson, it is recommended to use a device with a minimum of 2GB RAM.

Key Features

•Interactive Live Lessons in which students can ask the tutor questions in real-time through live chat, and benefit from questions asked by other students.

• Personalized learning experiences for learners in senior secondary school to encourage their deep & continued learning, and monitor their path to academic excellence. The app employs an individualistic approach to learning, applying simplified teaching methods designed to amplify each student’s learning ability with quality lesson plans from the best tutors.

• Timed Mock WAEC exams with step by step solutions.

• Quizzes and practice questions with detailed solutions to help students perfect their understanding.

• Relevant content built to specifically engage African students in a manner that is culturally relevant and responds to the syllabi in their respective countries. The learning content from the app is planned, executed, and reviewed by subject matter experts - using videos, interactive animations, quizzes, and assessments.


• The app also provides analytics and reporting data for parents and guardians to monitor the child’s academic growth and guide them with the optimization of the learning experiences.



Please call +2347000222333 or send an email to help@ulesson.com for feedback and support.

title: Airvet: Vet On Demand
description:
Airvet is on-demand pet care. FaceTime instantly with a live vet, anytime, anywhere. No waiting rooms, no fighting traffic. We'll connect you with a licensed veterinarian 24/7. So why use Airvet? Ok, picture this:

It's Wednesday at 2:27pm. You are just about to hop onto your 6th Zoom meeting for the day, when you realize that you never put away that picked over rotisserie chicken after lunch, so it’s just sitting out on the kitchen counter. You walk over to the kitchen and notice… no chicken. No trace of a chicken. Instead, you see Buddy, your rambunctious 3 year old german shepherd, sitting quietly, nay... obediently... in the center of the kitchen. At first you think, was there ever a chicken? Then Buddy hiccups and you realize, Buddy ate that WHOLE CHICKEN, bones and all. You lose your mind! Can a dog eat a bone? Will Buddy die a slow torturous death? Should you drive to the emergency room right now? Is there even one around me? How much is this going to cost? What should your Slack away status be? Emergency Dog Death? How much would that cost? Then you remember Airvet. You open the app and in seconds you’re on a FaceTime call with Dr. Lantry, and all of sudden, you feel calm. Buddy isn’t going to die, but you’re going to need to come up with that Slack away status. No more Costco chickens. 

Get the picture yet?

--HOW IT WORKS--
Download the Airvet app and start an on-demand video call with a licensed vet. Airvet is the easiest way to connect with a veterinarian for advice around all your pet questions. Our experts are real vets who specialize in pet health & wellness. No question is too small or silly - we can help! 
 
--GET STARTED--
- Download the Airvet app
- Create a Pet Profile for your pet
- Start a video call and connect with a licensed veterinarian in seconds
- Have follow up questions? No problem. Chat with the same vet from your video call for up to 3 days post call. Send texts, video, and photos.
 
--CALL ANYTIME & FROM ANYWHERE--
Say goodbye to waiting rooms. Airvet is available 24/7 including nights, weekends, and holidays too. Call from the park, your home, your AirBNB - wherever. We'll connect you with a licensed veterinarian in our network so you can get advice. 

--ANY ANIMAL--
Airvet’s licensed vets can take care of and help you with any animal: Dogs, Cats, Horses, Fish, Pigs, Cows, Lizards, Snakes, Frogs, and more!
 
--ANY AGE--
Airvet’s licensed vets can take care of and help you with an animal at any age: Young (Puppies & Kittens), Adult Animals, Senior Animals. 
 
 
--CONNECT WITH YOUR VET--
Is your vet on Airvet? You can add your vet to your Pet Profile to do a virtual re-check or post-op, get Rx refills, lab results, and so much more. Medical issues, behavioral questions, or just general pet advice from your most trusted source, your own vet!
 
--REAL VETS--
We work with licensed and pre-’vetted’ veterinarians. You can always trust the information you receive from an Airvet vet. 
 
--TRANSPARENT PRICING--
$30 flat fee for all on-demand calls. No time limits. Includes up to 3 days of follow up via chat. 
 
--PET WELLNESS--
Don't have an urgent question about your pet? Use Airvet for a virtual Wellness Exam. Chat with our vet experts about your pet's nutrition, diet, dental routine, behavioral issues, breed-specific medical concerns and more. Get recommendations for keeping your pet healthy!

--CUSTOMER SUPPORT--
How can we help? Our awesome customer support team is ready to help you at any time. Email us at support@airvet.com or tag us on social @airvet
 
--GET YOUR VET ON AIRVET--
If your veterinarian is not on Airvet or does not have telehealth or telemedicine services, Airvet can help! If you don’t have a veterinarian, we’ve got you covered. If you’d like us to sign your veterinarian up for Airvet, email us at hello@airvet.com and we will reach out to your preferred vet.

comments: I love the idea of this. My vet suggested I use this app to connect with them. I entered all the info in for myself and my pet but never got an option to call my vet . I have reached out several times for help but never heard back. Very frustrating
Quick response and great advice. It's awesome to be able to have a vet respond so quickly. I definitely will use them again and recommend anyone with a pet to use. Thank you Airvet!!

Airvet is user friendly. I am happy I didn't have to drive to vets office for follow up visit after pets surgery. My dog is recovering well from the surgery. No need to take her to the vets office. No waiting in line is a big plus.

It was amazing to have access to a vet at 5 on a Sunday. She was thorough, went through my options with me, told me most likely scenarios, and gave me peace of mind in a stressful time. Very thankful for this app.

title: Think Dirty
description:
Think Dirty is the easiest way to learn about the potentially toxic ingredients in your cosmetics and personal care products. It’s an independent source that allows you to compare products as you shop. Just scan the product barcode and Think Dirty will give you easy-to-understand info on the product, track dirty ingredients and shop for cleaner options 

• Barcode Scanning: over 350,000+ cosmetics and personal care products majority from Canada and the U.S. are currently in our database.

• Dirty Meter® a comprehensive rating is given, along with detailed (but easy-to-understand) information on ingredients, certifications, and health impacts.

• My Bathroom Rating: keep track of what’s already in your bathroom. Learn your current bathroom rating, and track your progress on “cleaning” it up.

• Shopping lists: save products to make shopping faster and easier.

• Buy it now: buy products directly from Amazon.com or Amazon.ca

• UPC Submission: Are we missing a product? Scan and submit a barcode for us to look into. For registered users who submitted products, we thank you and will notify you once they are in our database. 


As mentioned in:

25+ Apps To Make Your Everyday Life Easier – TED Blog

7 New Beauty Apps You Need to Download Now – Allure Magazine

26 Underrated Apps Every Twentysomething Should Download Right Now – BuzzFeed

The Beauty And Fashion Apps You Need To Download, ASAP – Glamour Magazine UK

As a small team, we are working diligently to accommodate the overwhelmingly positive amount of users' submissions (especially from our EU users) to our database. 

We appreciate constructive feedback. Please email us at questions@thinkdirtyapp.com if you have comments or suggestions.

comments: I only have the free version, and I don't frequently find the need to sort by paid category, as I usually do my own research and use this as a tool to help with specific products, not as a primary search platform. It is really helpful, but I wish it had less general explanations for some ingredients. I understand it is based off the listing from the manufacturer, but some of the ingredients are under an umbrella listing rather than specifically listed. Ex. Fragrance vs Essential Oils

Don't bother with this if you live outside of the USA. I live in the UK & tried to use it repeatedly. It didn't recognise any of the products I tried to scan/ stated they weren't in the database (this included products from The Body Shop. Not exactly a niche, unheard of brand). When I tried to manually enter each product (a complete ball ache) the app repeatedly crashed. Talks a lot about the FDA/ how the EU regs are better, so I suspect it would work in the US.

Good tool... Things to note though: To get all the perks, you'll need to buy the add-on (i didn't and still love it); Lots of products out there haven't been rated (but you can submit them); Some ingredient ratings are confusing (ex. natural fragrance has like 100 diff. names); Look out for reviews of products before buying (just because it's a '0' on the scale doesn't mean it's the best option out there😅).
Been a great app. Lots of things have been rated but also lots haven't that I have submitted. I love that I can't find a better substitute to toxic options. I tell lots of people about this app
Great resource - have been able to consistently change up products I was using to healthier alternatives - it's a challenge to get your bathroom shelf rating down, but worth it! Great app.

title: National Car Rental
description:
Tap into the power of the Emerald Club® with the National Car Rental® app. We’ve made the app better and faster than ever with features to help you take control of your rental experience on the go.

Speed & convenience in the palm of your hand

As an Emerald Club member, profile details are automatically applied so reservations are easier than ever
Access current and upcoming trip information as well as past rental history
Search National locations worldwide and view location details, like hours of operation, addresses and phone numbers – even get arrival directions to the lot
Contact roadside assistance or 24/7 customer support, and access frequently asked questions.

Tools for the Control Enthusiast

Rental Tracker℠ provides you with timely and important information about your rental when you need it.
Manage your Emerald Club profile, view your progress to the next Emerald Club tier and credits toward free rental days.
Extend your rental directly from the app by simply choosing a new return date.

Virtually everything you need to get on the road

With Emerald Checkout℠, you can take control to a whole new level at Emerald Aisle locations. Scan a vehicle in the aisle (and view details like mileage and features), confirm your rental options and accelerate your exit process with a Virtual Pass barcode.
Choose your vehicle from virtually anywhere with Virtual Aisle℠ (available at select locations). Upon arrival, use the app to choose a specific vehicle (with details like mileage and features) and we’ll hold it for 15 minutes so you can show your Virtual Pass, get the keys and go.

By clicking on "Install", you consent to the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy, including access to or storage of performance and usage of device and/or app related data for analytic purposes by National or its third-party providers.
Mobile Terms of Use: https://www.nationalcar.com/en_US/car-rental/app-terms-of-use.html

title: Flipboard - Latest News, Top Stories & Lifestyle
description:
Discover quality content for all your interests - from personalized news, entertainment, tech and sports articles to trending lifestyle magazines. We'll deliver the latest headlines, events, and entertainment stories to save you time, keep you informed and make sure you're always up-to-date with what's happening.

NEW: Flipboard TV - watch video from hundreds of publishers, TV stations and independent producers for free. Visit the Explore tab to select from 20 curated video channels for news, politics, travel, lifestyle, celebrity, sports and more.

Trust our unique combination of professional editors and smart algorithms to customize and deliver must-read stories and undiscovered gems. Get the full perspective on the latest news - and share what you find. Our editors blend expert voices and curated sources, and even recommended stories they know you'll like, so you can sit back and flip through what matters most to you. 

You can even customize your personalized newsstand: pick your passions and create a Smart Magazine for each topic feed. Are you interested in world news, events or tech developments? Want to read articles from national newspapers, discover sports podcasts, and skim the latest news? Looking to seize the zeitgeist from trending lifestyle stories? Flipboard has you covered. 

Plus, you can create personal magazines: find articles you want to read later or you want to share, and use the "+" to flip them into your own magazines. 

MAKE THE BEST USE OF YOUR TIME ON FLIPBOARD:

• Discover the latest news from The New York Times, National Geographic, Vanity Fair, and thousands more top newspapers and magazines, local, national or from around the world

• Create and customize your Smart Magazines: bundle together sources, people and even hashtags to get access to truly personalized news

• Customize your home feed: collate up to 9 of your favorite Smart Magazines together for quick access to the features you love

• Read The Daily Edition: keep up with the latest headlines and trending events in our daily roundup of important stories and personalized news articles

• Curate your perspective: collect stories around specific themes and add them to personal magazines

TOP PUBLISHERS ON FLIPBOARD:

- News & Politics: discover the latest headlines in national and world news, with newspapers and publications like The New York Times, CNN, Politico, Axios
- Tech & Science: read the latest tech news with TechCrunch, trending science stories with Wired, and more
- Business & Entrepreneurship: get personalized news relevant to your interests from The Wall Street Journal, Bloomberg, Forbes
- Sports: national pastimes or world news, never miss key sporting events with ESPN, CBS Sports
- Entertainment: get world news, even for celebrities and entertainment with People, Rolling Stone, Variety
- Lifestyle & Wellness: explore emerging lifestyle trends with Brit + Co., Self, Women's Health
- Food & Cooking: get some serious food inspiration from Bon Appetit, Food & Wine, Serious Eats
- Travel: feed your wanderlust with National Geographic, Travel + Leisure, Lonely Planet
- Home & Gardening: dream up your ideal home ELLE DECOR, House Beautiful
- Style: avant-garde or corporate with an edge... get sartorial inspiration from Vogue, Refinery29, W Magazine, GQ

KEEP UP WITH FLIPBOARD:

For product updates and the latest headlines from our blog, including tips on how to use Flipboard and interviews with actors, writers, musicians, and more. Follow us on:
www.twitter.com/@flipboard
www.facebook.com/Flipboard
https://www.linkedin.com/company/flipboard-inc-

For videos on how to use Flipboard, visit https://about.flipboard.com/tutorials/

Need help using the Flipboard app? Browse our help articles by opening Settings then Help & Feedback. Or, click the contact button at flip.it/help

comments: Nice interface. Though each type of device has a different user experience, (iOS, Android, MacOS), a little weird but each is still very good. I like the ability to add and subtract areas if interest. They mark ads/sponsored posts pretty well. Pretty speedy on all devices, even somewhat older ones. Overall a nice news agragator.

I've been using flipboard for years. Now like 80% of the content is videos. And NONE of those videos actually play. It's so weird. They have some new video set up, every time I click on a video, it doesn't play. Just black screen. Click on it, it goes to another black screen. So, two major problems rendering this app useless: 1. Nearly all news is now in the form of videos. I don't want videos. I want to read, and 2. Those videos don't even work. How do you not beta test this, Flipboard??

If I open a page on source like golf or mma or something like that, I get articles that cover something else entirely. I'm really annoyed that I spend more time reporting articles that are not on topic and I don't know why this hasn't changed in years of reporting these articles... Please do something about this.

Been using flipboard for quite some time since you can customize what news you see or just flip through all news. Biggest down side is tbe comment section is really subpar and broken up into different sections. Dont even bother commenting if you see 100 plus comments because your comment is lost at the bottom. Other than that is a nice app to see any news you want.

Can't share URL if you click a link inside an article. Steps to repro: 1. Tap into an article 2. Tap any link on the page that goes to a different site 3. Observe the top toolbar shrinks from several items to 2 items. 4. Tap the share button in that toolbar 5. Pick literally anything on share sheet. 6. See "Couldn't Share item" error every time. If you fix this bug lmk and I'll revise my review! Update: Flipboard denied this obvious, reproducible bug. Smh. Bug does not happen on ios.

title: HD Pakistan Independence Day Wallpaper 2017
description:
A top quality Pakistan flag live wallpaper! A perfect live wallpaper for celebrating Pakistan independence day or national day! Feel proud of your country? Let this Pakistan flag fly high in your phone! 

The main Independence Day ceremony takes place in Islamabad and Karachi, where the national flag is hoisted at the Presidential and Parliament buildings. It is followed by the national anthem and live televised speeches by leaders. Usual celebratory events and festivities for the day include flag-raising ceremonies, parades, cultural events, and the playing of patriotic songs. A number of award ceremonies are often held on this day and also a few days after the celebration. title: Financial independence
description:
This guide will walk you through the basics of Financial Independence but if something doesn’t fit for your life that’s ok. This is your journey and your life. Use the tips you find helpful and toss the rest. We know as a group we can get a little extreme (ok, a lot extreme), but our community is full of diverse and wonderful people. There is no one way to reach Financial Independence. 

What you will learn:

    • A Quick Summary
    • Savings rate
    • The 4% Rule “of Thumb?”
    • Lower Your Living Expenses
    • House Hacking
    • Travel Rewards
    • Eliminate Debt
    • Easy Ways To Reduce Other Expenses
    • Investment Philosophy
    • Employer Accounts
    • IRAs
    • Real Estate
    • Side Hustles
    • Get 1% better

Simply put, the goal of the FI movement is to save 25 times your annual expenses. It is thought that once you have this amount saved you can begin withdrawing enough from your investment accounts to cover your expenses. At this point, you would be considered “financially independent” and no longer need to work for money. Your time is your own.

Subject Mastery Academy

title: Houzz - Home Design & Remodel
description:
Whether you’re building, remodeling or decorating, Houzz has you covered.

Get the Best Design Ideas for Your Home
- Browse more than 20 million high-resolution photos of home interiors and exteriors. Choose by style, location or room, such as kitchen or bathroom.
- Save and share home design photos with friends, family and home professionals.
- Use the Sketch feature to annotate and draw directly on photos from Houzz.

Find, View and Buy Products for Your Home
- Shop from more than 10 million products and materials, including vanities, cabinets, lighting, furniture, tile and more for interior and exterior design.
- Read verified product reviews.
- Save up to 75% off during featured sales.
- Use Visual Match, our visual recognition technology, to discover and buy products and materials directly from home design photos on Houzz.
- Wondering what that sofa would look like in your living room? Select the View in My Room 3D feature and use the camera on your Android device to see how products would look in your space.

Find, Hire and Collaborate with the Best Home Professional for Your Home Renovation Project
- Connect with over 2.5 million active home improvement professionals, including architects, general contractors, interior decorators, repair professionals and more.

Read Articles From Our Editorial Staff and Design Experts
- Check out our biweekly Houzz Newsletter for engaging and informative articles, including home tours, full kitchen and bathroom remodeling guides, home renovation news, decorating tricks, organizing guides, designing for pets, gardening advice, interior design and decor, humor and everything in between.
- Watch Houzz TV to see original videos of inspiring homes, how-tos and more.

Get Advice On Your Home Remodel Project
- Discuss home design and renovation topics in our Advice section and get feedback from the Houzz community on your home renovation projects and design ideas.

The Houzz app topped The New York Times list of “best apps for home improvement.” The Washington Post called Houzz the “single best source" for finding inspiration. CNN named it the “Wikipedia of interior and exterior design.”

Use of the Houzz Android App and the the services provided through the Apps are subject to Houzz.com's terms of use: http://www.houzz.com/termsOfUse

To learn more about the permissions required to install the Houzz app, please visit Houzz support: https://support.houzz.com/entries/38179588-What-permissions-does-the-Houzz-app-require-

comments: Not mobile friendly. I love this website on my laptop but when it comes to the mobile use I have to log out and log back in every single time I use the APP. Tech suggested I uninstall and reload. That did not help. Just not very convenient to use on the go.

What happened to the save option? For some reason this app has changed and when I click save it puts it in the wrong idea book rather than giving me a choice. When I try to correct it I get a search box instead of my list of idea books so I have to try to remember all the exact names of my ideabooks and then there is no confirmation that the idea has been moved. The same problem exists when I go to an ideabook and try to move a pic to the correct ideabook. It is frustrating!

I love Houzz but the relentless sharing prompts are ANNOYING. I don't want to share everything I save - there should be a way to disable this feature. Seriously, I have no ambition to share anything with anyone yet I'm constantly prompted to share it with others. Enough already... I hate this feature.

There used to be line drawing tool within the create page. Now you just have a free hand pencil tool,and an arrow tool. How should one draw a straight line then??! There's no eraser as well. Dissapointed.

App requests too much user data. They even sell your data for "commercial purposes" AR feature isn't even AR. It's just an image over the camera. It sucks. This is just a data stealer. AND WHY DON'T I HAVE AN OPTION TO DELETE MY DATA???!!!!!

title: Google Play Books - Ebooks, Audiobooks, and Comics
description:
Google Play Books is the one app you need for enjoying audiobooks and ebooks purchased from Google Play.

Choose from millions of best selling ebooks, comics, textbooks, and audiobooks. Download your book to read or listen on the go. When you’re finished, find your next favorite from recommendations personalized just for you. Buy audiobooks and ebooks as you go - with no subscription required.

LISTEN TO A GREAT AUDIOBOOK ANYWHERE, ANYTIME
* New! Audiobooks are now available on Google Play
* Buy one or many - no monthly subscription required
* Preview free samples of audiobooks before you buy
* Pick up where you left off on Android, iOS, or on your web browser

MILLIONS OF EBOOKS AT YOUR FINGERTIPS
* Preview free samples from our catalog of millions of books
* Read your books, comics, and textbooks on Android, iOS, or your web browser, even when you’re offline
* Tap the page and watch your favorite comic book or manga come to life with Bubble Zoom
* Take notes that sync with your Google Drive and share them with a group for easy collaboration.
* Use the Night Light setting to automatically adjust the background color and brightness to make it easier for you to fall asleep

comments: I love this app. The Read Aloud function alone is worth the 5 * rating. In terms of research, this has been incredibly useful, I use the storage feature (it saves the highlights and notes to a file on your Google Drive) to go back to what I had previously found important. This is, perhaps, the most important app on my phone. Sure, it has some drawbacks but I am ever-so grateful for the ongoing work on this product.

It is a great app for read books and listen audiobooks. But in the shop section is an disadvantage. I live in Germany and I using a German smartcard, but although my mobile phone is set to English, I only get offers for German books. I have to search specifically for English speaking books, i can't brouse unselfconscious throughout the shop. There are still good offers for English speaking books after all.

I used this app for several years on my android tablet but recently all books in my library and samples are opening in unreadable formats: only a few pages at the beginning show and they are not aligned with the screen. They are cropped so that part of the page is unreadable. The rest of the pages in a book are blank. Google Play Help was useless in fixing this issue.

A very, very good app it does not require money to download and does not require your credit or debit card number for buyin free books the audio for audio books is very good and you can even change the page colours as per your eyes like. A very realistic flipping animation. Overall it's very awesome and I highly recommend you to download this.

Just purchased an ebook. Money has been deducted from my account and the transaction is shown to be successful. Yet I can't find my purchase anywhere, neither in the library nor in my purchase list. I can't even request for refund as I can't track the purchase from anywhere other than my own bank account transaction record. Very much disappointed. Would like to have my money back or never to make any purchase here again.

comments: I liked this app so much when it first came out. There continues to be a bug where when you enter a wager on the app, it sometimes enters it twice. The scoring updates are very slow. Sometimes the notifications arrive, and other times they don't. Sometimes this app works perfectly, and other times, it won't load at all when switching between leagues. If this could be improved, I would likely renew my EDGE subscription, despite the very poor betting advice. I really like entering wagers on the computer in order to reference them on the phone. That works perfectly.

If you just want to track your bets then this is 5 stars. Live game updates and alerts. The UI is buggy though so putting in your bets can take a little while unless your using a book that can be linked with them like Pointsbet. Also the promotional ads for sportsbooks sign ups are BS so don't bother falling for them. They got the commission and you don't get the crazy promo that you thought you were going to get

Had a few bugs when first installed, but were manageable for the info the app was streamlining. However the new update killed the convenience this app used to give the user. If I could revert back to the old version, even with those few bugs I would 5 star it though. *EDIT* Changed to 5 stars due to lack of competition in the industry for a simple bet tracker. Even though it may bug up at times I am still much happier using this app, than any other app out there. Competition will change rating.

On their app they had 59.99 annual membership fee which i paid. A month later I was charged 29.99. I immediately emailed them and was told at the time I signed up the MONTHLY was 59.99 a month and it was advertised as the annual which was a mistake. They had since dropped the monthly to 29.99. Bottom line is at the least they are engaging in false advertising. I would stay away from this app and would never recommend it to anyone.

After the updates the app is horribly slow and lags. it takes forever to put in your bets. it use to be my favorite but not now im looking for another app. Painfully slow. And it wont stay on what sport you pick like i cant log my basketball or hockey bets. it will only will show baseball games even when i pick nba it shows nba at the top, but all the games are baseball. wth. Fix the app. its horrible.

title: Asana: Your work manager
description:
Asana is the work manager for teams. But better. From the small stuff to the big picture, Asana organizes work so teams are clear what to do, why it matters, and how to get it done.

✔ TAKE THE GUESSWORK OUT OF WORK
See who is doing what and by when across the whole team:
Coordinate plans, projects, and tasks in one shared space
Switch between list, kanban board, and calendar views
Organize and assign tasks; set due dates
Attach files to tasks so relevant info is easy to find

✔ GET THE WHOLE PICTURE—EVEN ON THE GO
Keep an eye on progress no matter where you are:
Instantly see if projects are on track, at risk, or off track—and why
Post status updates, or request updates from project owners
Drill down into tasks for more information

✔ PUSH WORK ALONG...WITHOUT GETTING PUSHY
Make sure nothing falls through the cracks:
Clarify if tasks are high, medium, or low priority
Approve work or mark tasks for approval
Set tasks as milestones to establish critical checkpoints
Get notified when tasks are completed, overdue, and more

✔ ASANA MOBILE + WEB = YOUR A-TEAM
Work efficiently whether you’re at the office or on the go: 
Automatically transcribe voice memos to tasks
Convert photos of whiteboards, charts, or diagrams to tasks
Instantly sync work between the app and web
Work offline without worrying about losing your data

Join more than 75,000 organizations and millions of users worldwide who trust Asana to stay organized and in control of their work. Download the Asana app now.

By downloading Asana, you agree to our Terms of Service, which you can find at https://asana.com/terms

title: StubHub - Live Event Tickets
description:
StubHub is the top destination for buying and selling tickets to the world's best events. Ticket prices may be higher or lower than face value.

MLB, NBA, NHL, and concert tickets at your favorite venue and more – StubHub has your tickets for amazing experiences! Over 10 million upcoming live sports events, concerts, theater shows, gigs and tours are available. 

StubHub recently ranked #1 in Newsweek’s America’s Best Customer Service in 2019. Tickets orders are 100% guaranteed, with customer service all the way to your seat. Get a coupon worth 120% of your original order if an event is cancelled.

Get tickets for your favorite MLB, NBA, NHL team, theater show or music concert from the day they go on sale to the day of the event. See the venue and find out which artists are performing from your phone.

Buy event tickets using the largest ticket selection with StubHub! Concerts, MLB, NBA, NHL tickets, local shows and more.

Sell tickets easily right from the StubHub app if you have a change of plans. 
STUBHUB FEATURES

• Event Recommendations: Let the fun find you with event recommendations based on your Spotify account, downloaded music, and favorite artists and teams
• Friends: Find out what your friends are into and which events they’re going to
• Interactive venue maps: See the view before you buy on selected maps
• Virtual venue View: Get an immersive, 3-D view from your section for selected venues
• Google Pay: Speed through checkout with Google Pay (US events only)
• Mobile tickets: Get in with your phone – no need to print!*
• Wear OS by Google: View your tickets, find events and more, just by looking at your wrist
• Venue and artist info: Check on upcoming events and discover similar artists
• Ticket price alerts: Tell us what you want to pay and get notified when there’s a match
• My tickets: Track your orders, view your mobile tickets and get ready for your next event
• Sell tickets: List tickets, manage your listings and view your sales
• Event categories: View events by category to discover events based on your interests or mood. Concerts, NBA games, comedy shows and more.
• Barcode scanning: Attract more buyers and keep tickets you're selling listed for longer by scanning ticket barcodes*

Buy and resell tickets for local events with StubHub. Download now!

*Available for selected teams and venues

title: Toca Life World: Build stories & create your world
description:
Create stories and build your own world with Toca Life World. You’ll get all the fun of your other favorite Toca Life apps such as City, Vacation, Office, Hospital, and more, all together in one place. 

INTRODUCING TOCA LIFE WORLD
Want to give grandma a wild hairstyle? Bring a sloth to the Skate Park? Or just hang out with friends? If you thought it was fun to dive into a Toca Life app and do whatever you want then you were right. This is your own world where you build characters and create stories your way. Make storylines and discover that anything is possible today. 

You can even go further and create stories with your favorite characters in any location you want. Want to take a pet to School? Go for it. Take the doctor to the Salon and dye her hair green? Rock on. In Toca Life World you’re the boss. Build characters, create stories, and play the way you want.

MAKE STORYLINES, BUILD CHARACTERS & CREATE YOUR OWN WORLD - WHY YOU’LL LOVE TO PLAY TOCA LIFE WORLD

FIRST 8 LOCATIONS & 39 CHARACTERS INCLUDED
You can visit Bop City, a vibrant city area with 8 different locations for you to discover, like the hairdresser, the shopping mall and food court, or even an apartment. It’s a great start when you want to build your own world!

KEEP THE TOCA LIFE APPS YOU ALREADY HAVE
Do you already play other apps within the Toca Life series? City? Vacation? Office? Great! When you download Toca Life World, we’ll help you bring all of that stuff into the mega-app. Then you can start mixing and matching locations and characters to create heaps of new storylines. 

BUY NEW LOCATIONS AND CHARACTERS
If you want to discover more locations, that’s cool. Toca Life World has a shop where more than 50 locations, 300 characters, and 125 pets are available for purchase. With different prices from small to big, you can decide to add a little or a lot. We’ll always be updating with more locations, characters and crazy things to do.

GIFTS EVERY WEEK
Guess what? You don’t need to make purchases in the shop to get new items to add to your world. Check back every week and discover exclusive surprise gifts!

Discover exciting storylines, build characters, and don’t miss out on a moment of fun - download Toca Life World today! 

About Us:

At Toca Boca, we believe in the power of play to spark kids’ imaginations and help them learn about the world. We design our products from the kids' perspective to empower kids to be playful, to be creative and to be who they want to be. Our products include award-winning apps that have been downloaded more than 200 million times in 215 countries and offer fun, safe, open-ended play experiences. Learn more about Toca Boca and our products at tocaboca.com.

Privacy is an issue that we take very seriously. To learn more about how we work with these matters, please read our privacy policy: https://tocaboca.com/privacy

description:
Get ready for a new,original, challenging matching pairs game.
You need to Match 3D objects on the ground and pop them all ! When you clear a level, you will find new objects to pair.

Match 3D is easy to play for everyone !

Polished pairs of animals, foods, school objects, house properties, emoji's and much more to satisfying levels to pass with just onet the cards!

title: Newsvoice - Unbiased & Real News Feed, USA & World
description:
The first news app to combine technology and community, giving you the world’s highest rated, custom news feed - unbiased and tailored to your needs and interests. In-depth reporting on the 2020 US presidential election.

We aggregate reports from major news sites, as well as international and independent media. All sources are conveniently listed under each news summary and every source is tagged with its political leaning. Anyone can write unbiased summaries - our professional journalists and moderators review every edit to keep the highest quality.

The news is broken
In US news, 9 out of 10 reports are controlled by only five corporations. Unbiased news with no political leaning, and different perspectives, is insanely hard to find. It’s time to fix journalism. Together.

Change the news – the world will follow
What we hear and read affects everything in our lives - the food we eat, the things we buy, the people we trust and vote for. The news shapes how we think about the world. When we are in control and get the real news, we make better choices, we hold power to account, we elect better leaders, we can even stop wars.

Stay truly informed
In your custom news feed you see the latest, top and trending, real news, with all their sources listed, for the ultimate convenience. You spend less time and effort on staying truly informed. With unbiased summaries written by our readers and vetted by our journalists, it’s quick and effortless to find the independent reports that truly matter.

Be part of a movement
Newsvoice is built and shaped by our community. As a news reader, you can upvote stories that you find important, and more people will see them. Everyone can add stories and sources that are missing. For the first time ever, there is an entirely open and democratized platform for honest journalism. Together we will build it into the largest and best unbiased news app on the planet.

Give and gain valuable insight
Discuss the latest with our news readers. Share your knowledge and opinion or simply see another angle. With thousands of comments per day, we work hard to feature the well written ones, and save you time and blood pressure.

Try a new approach
News apps, aggregators and websites have streamlined journalism, and the sad result is click bait, bias and a lack of truth. We are not another news app. We give you all the angles.

Experience new levels of convenience
All link sources in your news feed are arranged and carefully tagged with their domain and political leaning.

Support radical transparency
Our process and decision making will always be open and we love when our news readers, give suggestions and constructive feedback on how we do and can do things better. We are all in this together.

Keep up with Newsvoice
Need help using the news app, or have suggestions? Drop us a line or two at info@newsvoice.com

Let’s fix the news. Together.

comments: I like that it puts news in one place, but the bias markers are too simple to be useful. Particularly for foreign news, where the only bias is the continent of origin. I'd like to know where the news comes from, AND it's tilt, preferably with more accuracy than left/right/center. I'd like to know what other readers thought the bias was on average.

I genuinely enjoy looking at the news with this app. All of the stories are quickly summarized for a quick read and all have multiple sources from different perspectives if you want more information and for easy fact checking. You can also customize what kind of news hits your feed. Overall a very enjoyable app.

The app so far is really good and works fine on my Pixel on Android 11. The crowd sourced headline and summary idea is very interesting. I don't feel qualified to contribute, but with more users that will get easier I'm sure. It's a very good way to get news. Even just reading the headlines is enjoyable. I don't feel like I'm being toyed with. The summaries so far have been very impressive for how they're made. You can tell a lot of thought went into them.

Amazing app!! It's definitely the kind of "one stop shop" that people who like to pay attention to the news would find very helpful. It's got links to multiple news outlets and tells you their ideological tinge and location so that you can be pre-preparred for the tilt of the story. This is a great way to help people stay informed and be aware of any bias that they will be exposed to.

Works pretty well so far. I wish you could see the bias of sources articles from different nations, instead of the flag just being the country or region itself. Aside from that, I like how I get notifs that keep me updated on the latest happenings, especially ones I might be interested in

title: Notarize
description:
Operational 24 hours per day, 7 days per week. Average wait time is less than one minute. 

Upload a document, prove your identity, fill out your document, and connect with a licensed Virginia electronic notary by live video call. Sign before the agent who will then legally notarize your document.

When done, share your document by email, save to dropbox, or print and submit manually. 

If your document is in paper form, Notarize offers the ability to scan your document directly within the app.

Notarize agents are held to the highest standards and have completed training, undergone background checks, and independently hold insurance in accordance with notary industry best practices. All Notarize agents are licensed electronic notaries located in Virginia. 

The service is based on Virginia Senate Bill 827 and House Bill 2318, which were passed in 2011 and allow for remote electronic notarization. The service is across the country due to the Full Faith and Credit Clause of the U.S. Constitution as well as laws in every state that explicitly accept out of state notarizations. 

Simply download the app to legally notarize your document today.

title: Word of Life Hawaii
description:
The Word of Life App features encouraging content from Pastors Art & Kuna Sepulveda, the senior pastors of Word of Life in Honolulu, Hawaii. 

Word of Life is a church you can call home. We are a place that promotes your progress and joy in believing. This app provides access to messages from our pastors, including joining our services live from Hawaii, that will help people become fully devoted followers of Christ.

For more information about our church, visit our website at www.wordoflifehawaii.com.

The Word of Life Christian Center App was created with The Church App by Subsplash.

title: Petfinder Adoptable Pets
description:
Find dogs, cats, puppies and kittens and filter by location, breed, age, size and gender. View profiles of more than 14,000 adoption groups. 
“Favorite” profiles, share them with friends, and find the perfect match for you!
WHAT ARE THE FEATURES AND BENEFITS OF ADOPTING ON PETFINDER? 

-    BROWSE ANIMALS: Find dogs, cats, puppies, kittens, rabbits, birds, horses, fish & more!  
  
-    FILTER RESULTS: Find a dog or cat by filtering the breed, age, size, gender, shelter/rescue
  
-    REVIEW PET DETAILS: Read the pet's information, including their bio descriptions 
  
-    SWIPE PET FAVORITES: Browse, ‘Like’, or ‘Pass’, swiping right to ‘Fav’ and left to ‘Pass’ 
  
-    INTRODUCE A PET TO FRIENDS: Share pets with friends or family via email or social media
  
-    THOUSANDS OF SHELTERS IN ONE SPOT: Search shelters and rescues to see their pets
  
PETFINDER HELPS BROWSE ADOPTABLE PETS IN YOUR AREA BY: 
  
-    SPECIES: Find a dog, a cat, a puppy, or a kitten. Looking to adopt a bird, fish, reptile or barnyard animal? Search Petfinder according to ‘species’ so as to specifically filter animal type
  
-    BREED: View the most common dog breeds and find the right dog breed for you. Learn more about hypoallergenic dogs, small dog breeds, hairless dogs, and the best dogs for kids. Also, view the most common cat breeds and find the right cat for you. Find articles about hairless cats, hypoallergenic cats, cutest cat breeds, and the best cat breeds for kids
  
-    AGE: All ages of pets are available, from baby animals to adult pets, to every age in between
  
-    GENDER: Male and female
  
-    SIZE: Extra small, small, medium, large, and extra-large
  
-    COLOR: Adoptable pets not only have colorful personalities, but they also come in a wide variety of colors, when you take into consideration all of the variety of fur, feathers, and scales
  
-    KID-FRIENDLY: Learn more about the best kid-friendly dogs, cats, and animals
  
-    ANIMAL-FRIENDLY: Find out if your favorite animals are also friendly with other animals
 
-    AND MORE: The Petfinder blog articles enrich a pet parent's understanding of their pets
 
 
FOLLOW PETFINDER ON SOCIAL MEDIA
 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Petfinder/ 
  
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/petfinder/?hl=en 
  
Twitter: https://twitter.com/petfinder?lang=en

comments: After most recent update I am unable to use the app, the screen doesn't click/scroll EDIT: After update app works phenomenally! Thanks! Revised to 5 🌟

This app is the best ever if your like me. You love animals. Want them as pets and most importantly to me you actually save the animals life and do a little bit of good for these voiceless, helpless creatures who only want is for someone to love them! It has all sorts of filters you can use to locate the type, age, breed and it will tell you if they are already housebroken. Most of the time the animal will be sterilized, disease tested and even microchipped so if lost its easily recovered.

Signed into this using my Google account, but when when I use that method on the actual website, the accounts are not the same, none of my favorites. No app option to login with email, just Google or Facebook. Very frustrating. No clear way to save fav searches in app, and there's nothing in the settings that let you confirm your email or any other info. Really poor usability. Feels like it's not trying to work with the site and is detrimentally bare bones.

The app used to work great. Now almost every day when I go into the app it logs me out. It struggles to log me in and when I finally log in it doesn't have any of my favorited animals. It's very frustrating because I have to go back and favorite them. There's no point now because it's just going to log me out again and get rid of my favorites.

Was working great on my Note 9 until the most recent update. Now, whenever I try to favorite or unfavorite a pet, it crashes. It also doesn't show that a pet you favorited is unavailable until you look at their details. I can't log in with my email either, like I can do on my computer, only Facebook or Google.

title: CHAIR YOGA
description:
Chair yoga is for those who might be struggling due to age, certain types of disabilities or inflexibility in general. It's also ideal for those that spend a lot of their time sitting down  and might be in need of some office yoga or are in crowded places wishing to reap the rewards from this exercise. 

This is also an ideal type of yoga for seniors as its gentle and easily accessible for all. 
What's particularly great about this type of yoga is , it's simple , doable & all in the comfort of your own home , or in your office / work space. All you need is a chair and some spare time! Chair yoga is simply yoga but in a chair... you literally replace a yoga mat for that chair but continue to take the advantage of great fitness and better health that come's from doing some of these seated yoga poses. 

It has also been known to help those with MD and CP feel not only physically healthy but also mentally fit and even happier!  Once someone, who hasn’t had the ability or chance to really work on their physical bodies are able to do so it does something for their mental health also. Stop and think about how wonderful you feel when you accomplish something you have wanted to do for awhile.  All of a sudden you feel proud, proud of yourself and what you were able to do!

Imagine you have always had difficulty moving, stretching and working your body because of a physical disability.  Someone tells you or shows you this new method of yoga and suddenly you are able to not only move your body but you feel better about it!
So when it comes to chair yoga remember; go slow, learn from someone who knows what they are doing so that you don’t hurt yourself, check out your community center and locally, do some research online and see what you can find in your area.  If you would rather work out in your own home see it there isn’t a PT (physical therapist) in your area that would come in and help you, make sure they know exactly what you are looking for and that they are qualified to teach you Chair Yoga.

Included in this App: 

- Who Chair Yoga Is Useful For
- The Benefits of Chair Yoga & Why Everyone Should Be Doing This
- 8 Gentle Yoga Poses - Ideal For Beginners
- Simple Chair Yoga Poses To Ease Back Pain
- Seated Yoga Senior Poses for Those Suffering With Osteoarthritis 
- Easy Chair Yoga Workout For Seniors 
---And More

Chair yoga has something for everyone and can benefit those with muscular skeletal issues as well as those who spend most of their time in a chair, wheels or otherwise. Yoga has been around for many years and has helped to keep those who are committed to it keep fit, lose weight, be more flexible and even is used by Physical and Occupational therapists in helping their patients keep fit or heal more quickly.

Few people stop to think about the fact that chair yoga also offers wonderful health benefits. Yoga  in general has been shown to improve overall health, prevent and (even in some cases) reverse disease when practiced regularly as a lifestyle. With this in mind, it’s no surprise that it chair yoga itself can lend its benefits to those with mobility issues. 

App Features: 

- Regular Updates
- In-Depth Guide & Explanations
- Easy To Read
- Simple Navigation

comments: I was very disappointed in this app! While there is decent written information (the only reason it got one star), there are VERY FEW PICTURES!!!!! And what pictures they have are very simple and not linked to any of the poses discribed. For an app that is supposed to be for beginners to chair yoga --- don't you think we might need pictures or even video to help us understand the poses!!
Room for improvement. Photos are dark and mot clear. Drawings are better. First set of exercises had no pictures?
Too much explaining on how to but no pictures to go with explanations.
I like the concept but the app is not well designed.
Works right out of the chute!

comments: As others have said, the app is currently broken. You can only sign in after you reset your password, and even if you do, the app fails to load upcoming trips. Other things are customer unfriendly. For example, if I want to cancel a trip, you now have to chat with a bot (versus just being able to do a simple "click-and-cancel" request). I understand that it may help Expedia's contact deflection measures, but it feels needlessly complicated.

As of October 2020, the app has gotten much worse. Don't bother with it. Original comments: Works, but limited. You get a lot more choices on the webpage than you do in the app; so shopping for travel is mediocre. However, great to have your itineraries on the app. It would be nice if it stored full itineraries locally in case no connection.

Was a pretty good app. Now will not show trips after you book them.. dates change between starting seach and booking. Have had several booking only to show up to hotel or car rental place to find out my booking dates are wrong sometimes days weeks and even months away from the dates I chose. Expedia points not worth the hassles of miss placed bookings maybe time to use a new service if they don't fix this soon!!! Ridiculous that these bugs lasted more then a few days....

The app is very broken. When I open it I am greeted to a screen that is flashing and not responsive. When I go to close the app it opens back up and I have to fight with it. It was a good app before all this mess. Best part is my trip is in 3 days and I'm stuck using the browser on my cell phone. Just fix it.

I rated this app earlier 5 star because it used to work really smooth. Now whenever I try to log in, it makes me do the image authentication plus makes me log in again. I liked it when it was simple and kept me logged on. I want to give it 5 star, so please help me with this so I can update this rating.

title: Homelife Care Family App
description:
Cox Homelife Care uses smart devices to help seniors retain their independence and put their families at ease.

Homelife Care’s base kit includes professionally monitored smart devices like a hub and an automatic fall detection pendant that allow seniors to live independent and connected lives. With Homelife Care, help is never too far away if you ever need it; Homelife Care has 24/7 professional care, as our trained professionals are available and ready to assist around the clock.
 
Built for current Cox Homelife Care customers and their caregivers, the Homelife Care Family app sends alerts and insights that give caregivers peace of mind about their aging loved ones. The app alerts caregivers in the event of an emergency, sends medication reminders, and sends alerts if equipment batteries are low. Peace of mind is built into the Homelife Care Family App, and it even allows caregivers to stay informed without disturbing their senior loved ones.

Note: To use this app, you must be a current Cox Homelife Care customer.

title: Deepstash - Self Improvement, Motivation & Care
description:
Think of Deepstash as your personal library of thoughts and knowledge. A daily source of inspiring & life changing stories and ideas. Read articles, learn skills, get productivity tips and discover life hacks. All curated by our team and presented to you in a simple, practical and easy to remember, short summarized format. Fuel your curiosity and get smarter daily.

It's like your social media feed, if your social media feed had things that mattered :-)

Content & articles that matter to you. Our team curates the best stories around the web (articles, videos, podcasts & more, from top publications and magazines like Medium, Inc, Lifehacker, Forbes, Mark Manson, FastCompany, BBC, Tony Robbins & more) and provides actionable and inspiring short form key insights to improve yourself personally and professionally. A wealth of self help knowledge in your pocket.

Have questions? You’ll surely get answers by reading, learning and exploring a world of hard and soft skills as well as interests like time management, self improvement, leadership, self-confidence, motivation or psychology, that will make you a great fit anywhere in life you put your mind to.

Summarized ideas. You need just 5 minutes per day. Our team works for you. We provide a summary of the main insights of articles and other web content in a short and crisp 100 words or less format we call “ideas”.

Escape the negativity and time wasting pull of social media platforms. Our app’s goal is to help you towards self improvement and self care and to get you motivated, inspired, wiser and productive.

Personalized content & feed. Choose a few topics of interest (like self improvement, time management, problem solving, love & relationships & more) and then just use the app at your leisure. As you save ideas and use our app, we learn what you like and find the best stories and articles to show you every day, so you’re motivated and inspired. You don’t even have to work for it.

The more you save ideas the better we learn what articles and topics you love. We refresh your recommendations multiple times a day so you never run out of fresh stories and ideas.

title: TerraTime 🌎🕓 World Clock
description:
Start with a visually stunning virtual Earth in the palm of your hand: Real satellite photos drive a live simulation of day/night, clouds, seasons, sun, moon and more. Then, our unique clock and compass track the local movements and transitions of the sun and moon. It’s everything you need to stay connected to the world you live in.

And not just your local time: create a list of locations to show on the globe, and now this beauty is a world clock, too. See it all at a glance: not just what time it is in other places, but how those times relate to each other. It's the nature of time.

Lots of extras complete the picture: alarms, augmented reality, home screen widgets, live wallpapers, Wear OS watch faces. There’s no other app like TerraTime.

Superbly stylish, incredibly detailed and unbeatably useful - LifeOfAndroid.com
TerraTime is unique. It is bold and different... - AndroidApps Review
Possibly the most beautiful phone app I’ve seen. Highly recommended. - AndroidAstronomer.com
The overall beauty of the app is well, its beauty! - CoolSmartPhone.com
It's spot-on no matter where you look at it in the world - The Sun (UK newspaper)

Great for travelers, astronomers, weather watchers, geographers, teachers, photographers, fishermen and other outdoor types - as well as just about any geek you can think of.

Here’s what TerraTime includes:
• Easily shows any location, any date, any time
• Daylight clock and compass show sunrise & sunset; twilight & transit times; moon phase, rise & set
• Multiple clock/compass styles (currently Material, Classic, Wave, and Ouroboros)
• Independent time zone data: more up-to-date than what your phone has
• Globe and map depict real-time night-side shadow (on both Earth and Moon)
• Photorealistic simulations include clouds, city lights, sea ice, and more, generated from actual satellite imagery
• Globe and map are fully interactive, using touchscreen or device sensors
• AR View plots sun and moon paths in augmented reality (on supported devices)
• Clock and globe widgets for your home screen
• Live wallpapers for real-time map and globe
• Wear OS watch faces (4 styles), complications (10), and tiles (2)

This is the Free + No advertising
 + Additional locations (you get 3 for free)
 + Unlimited access to dynamic satellite overlays for clouds, polar sea ice, and surface imagery
 + Alarms you can set for any time zone - or for sunrise, sunset, etc. at any location

Please, if you have any issues, email us! There’s a link in the app’s About screen.
