title: Chime - Mobile Banking
description:
Welcome to banking made awesome. 

Chime is mobile and online banking with no hidden fees: get your paycheck up to 2 days early* with direct deposit, have fee-free overdraft when you’re in a pinch, grow your savings automatically, and manage your finances like a boss using the highly-rated Chime mobile banking app.

When you bank with Chime, you get a Visa® Debit Card, a Spending Account, and an optional Savings Account to help you save money. 

Applying for an account is free, takes less than 2 minutes and it won’t affect your credit score!

Here’s what our members love most about Chime:
• Get your paycheck up to 2 days early* with direct deposit
• Fee-free overdraft.** We’ll spot you on debit card purchases with no overdraft fees. 
• No hidden fees: no monthly fees, no overdraft fees, no foreign transaction fees, no minimum balance requirements 
• Over 38,000 fee-free ATMs with Moneypass and Visa Plus Alliance
• Real-time transaction notifications
• Daily balance alerts
• Block your card instantly in-app
• Grow your savings automatically with our Savings Account
• Send money instantly with Pay Friends to other Chime members. 
• Deposit checks using Mobile Check Deposit for eligible members.^ 
• Apple Pay™ / Google Pay™ for when you forget your wallet
• Move money between your other bank accounts
• EMV chip card security
• Friendly and responsive customer support

With the Chime mobile banking app, you can stay in control of your money. Track your spending, link your other bank accounts, and save money.

How to switch banks:
• Step 1: Open Your Account: Download the app and sign up. Once approved, we’ll send you your Chime card within two weeks!
• Step 2: Fund Your Account: Set up a direct deposit with your employer or payer to have funds deposited to your Chime account every payday. You can also connect other bank accounts and transfer funds from your existing bank account.
• Step 3: Update Bill Payments: Activate your card when it arrives, add it to Apple Pay, and set up recurring bill payments with your Chime card number or with your Chime Spending Account and routing numbers.

 For more information please visit www.chime.com.

***Learn how we collect and use your information by visiting our Privacy Policy at https://www.chimebank.com/policies/chime/privacy-policy/.***

Banking services provided by, and debit card issued by, The Bancorp Bank, or Stride Bank, N.A., Members FDIC, pursuant to a license from Visa U.S.A. Inc. Debit card may be used everywhere Visa debit cards are accepted.

*Early access to direct deposit funds depends on the timing of payer’s submission of deposits. We generally post such deposits on the day they are received which may be up to 2 days earlier than the payer’s scheduled payment date.
**Chime SpotMe is an optional, no fee service that requires that you receive $500 in direct deposit a month to qualify to overdraw your account up to $20 on debit card purchases. Chime, in its sole discretion, may allow you to withdraw your account up to $100 or more based on your Chime Account history, direct deposit history and amount, spending activity and other risk-based factors. Your Limit will be displayed to you within the Chime mobile app. You will receive notice of any changes to your Limit. Your Limit may be increased or lowered at any time by Chime.
^Not all new or existing customers are eligible to use Mobile Deposit. There are qualifications and enrollment requirements for participation in Mobile Deposit, and we reserve the right to change the qualification and enrollment requirements in our sole discretion at any time without prior notice. We may require you to upload a picture of your driver’s license or other identifying documents prior to using Mobile Deposit. Eligibility requirements can be found online after you have signed into your Spending Account.

recentChanges: Happy Halloween! If you're not out trick or treating, you can have fun reading up on our latest release notes. Instead of leaving you with some tricks, we're leaving a few treats in the form of bug fixes.
comments: amazing bank. love the instant notifications and easy direct deposits. very simple to use. Update: 10/20 Go with a real bank. This bank enjoys doing random maintenance on all accounts. Completely disabling your account for DAYS at a time. So far my account has been disabled for 2 days. There's plenty of money in my account, I just can't use any of it. Dropped to 3 stars simply because it's a free bank account. That's the only good thing about Chime. Its free. They just control your money.

My experience with Chime overall has been a great one. Instead of getting paid on Fridays, I get paid on Wednesdays every week via direct deposit. Two days early! Chime also offers the SpotMe feature, which is basically overdraft protection with no fees. Another cool feature for this being a virtual bank, is you have the option to set up a Secured Credit Builder Card with no pre-set credit limit, up to $10,000. I'm on the waitlist right now, but from what I read, it sounds very helpful!

More honest review today, today marks the third time in two months that time bank has frozen, has had technical difficulties and has no one available to up to talk to customers for hours on end. Now yes time is convenient, but there are other cards like it on the market. Which I am now starting to look into, as well as brick and mortar building type banks because unfortunately I can't let this keep happening especially not during the holiday season.

I have had this mobile banking app for over 6 years and haven't had any problems but recently their have been outages causing the app to be unavailable and my money unusable! I'm extremely furious that they can't keep their app working properly so I can use MY MONEY! Currently waiting for the app to be available so I can take my money and go to another bank! This is outrageous and you get no compensation for the late payments or overall difficulty of not being able to use YOUR MONEY!

I would be rating this higher, but for some reason I am not being shown a history of my purchases on the app. My girlfriend doesn't seem to be having this issue, only me. I have double checked to ensure that I have the most recent update, which I do. I cannot determine the cause for this. Any advice or assistance would be appreciated. The 'support bot' has not been any help at all. Thanks.

title: Footsteps2Brilliance School Edition
description:
*** This application requires a Footsteps2Brilliance®, Inc. membership, which you get through your school district. 

With our eBooks and games available in English and Spanish, Footsteps2Brilliance®, Inc. is the most flexible bilingual program around. With audio support, clear and simple instructions and checks for understanding, Footsteps2Brilliance®, Inc. is ideally suited to meet the needs of English Language Learning (ELL) students.

•	Reports for parents to track their children’s progress

title: Zombies, Run! (Free)
description:
Get ready for the run of your life. Join 5 million runners on an epic adventure!

You tie your shoes, put on your headphones, take your first steps outside. You’ve barely covered 100 yards when you hear them. They must be close. You can hear every guttural breath, every rattling groan - they’re everywhere. Zombies. There’s only one thing you can do: Run!

Zombies, Run! is an ultra-immersive running game and audio adventure, co-created with award-winning novelist Naomi Alderman. Every run becomes a mission where you’re the hero, with our immersive audio drama putting you at the centre of your very own zombie adventure story. While you run to the perfect mix of heart-pumping audio drama and pulse-pounding songs from your own playlist, you’ll collect supplies to grow your base back home. 

BBC NEWS - “The only way to save yourself is to run for real.”
WIRED - “In the style of Runkeeper, with an exciting undead twist.”
LIFEHACKER - “A really cool way to get outside and exercise.”
CNN - “Turns exercise into a game - a terrifying, terrifying game.”
TIME - "Takes all the fun of a zombie game and funnels it into a fitness app."

WALK, JOG, OR RUN ANYWHERE
Zombies, Run! works anywhere and at any speed. You can jog in a park, run along a beach, or walk along a trail. It even works on treadmills! 

YOU ARE RUNNER 5 
Hundreds of lives are counting on you. You’ve got to rebuild your base from a few shivering survivors into a fortified beacon of civilization by collecting critical supplies and avoiding roving zombie hordes. Can you save them and learn the truth about the zombie apocalypse?

A WORLD OF STORIES
You become the hero in an epic story of humanity’s struggle for survival where your running *really* matters, and there’s a deeper mystery to be uncovered as well. Play the first four missions for free and unlock one extra mission every week. 

JOIN THE ABEL RUNNER'S CLUB
Unlock all 300+ story missions immediately for unlimited play, plus Interval Training and Airdrop Mode. Membership is available for $5.99 USD/month or $34.99 USD/year. Your subscription will automatically renew. (Existing paid players will have access to a special discounted membership rate, plus free access to all game modes and S1-3 missions).

YOUR OWN MIX
Choose your own custom playlists before you start running: the story unfolds in between your tracks through a series of dynamic radio messages and voice recordings.

ZOMBIES CHASES
Saving the world not exciting enough? Activate Chases to kick things up a notch. When you hear zombies on your six, it’s time to speed up before they get too close. Can you escape every mob, or will you have to drop some of your hard-earned supplies to distract them? There’s only one way to find out.

DETAILED STATS
View detailed graphs and stats for your entire running and game progress — and check out which songs you play the most while escaping zombies!

KEEP THE SURVIVORS ALIVE
Every time you run, you’ll automatically collect vital supplies like medicine, batteries and food. Once you’re home, you can use them to build your very own post-apocalypse community. Do you strengthen your defences against the zombies, or build a new farm? Share the results with your friends and find out who can make the brightest future for humanity.

WORKS WITH WEAR OS BY GOOGLE
Check your run progress and speed at a glance with our Wear OS app. Now you can escape the zombies without fumbling with your phone!

VIEW YOUR RUNS ONLINE WITH ZOMBIELINK
Register with our free ZombieLink service to view and share your runs online, complete with maps and full run history!


NOTES 
- Requires Android 5.0 or above
- Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life. 

Follow us at @zombiesrungame and visit zombiesrungame.com

comments: motivating, fun, exciting and immersive! I adore the detailed audio when incoming zombies or distant gunfire sound as if they're truly getting closer with your pace. "Letters" will also be e-mailed to you as you journey through this story. The free version is worthwhile for those looking to enjoy this a couple times a week, since it takes a few days to unlock each episode. Whereas subscription is worth it when you're looking to progress almost daily like myself. I love it!

My favorite running app but... I like it for the entertainment. While the app is much less glitchy for legacy users than before, the distance is way off. I can walk slowly and it will say that I have done a mile every 6 minutes, when I have walked maybe half a mile or less. However, I do love the incentive to run when I have the Zombie chases on, it gets me going and has helped to make much progress.

I love Zombies! Run!! I started running from zombies with the Abel gang in 2018, and never stopped. I only got 2 episodes into Season 1 before I started my subscription, and it has been worth every penny! This is the ONLY app that I cannot think of one single critical comment about. The stories are interesting, the actors are extremely talented, and if the need to find out "what happened next" doesn't get you moving, nothing will. Thank you, Six to Start!

I just love this app, it got me running outside for the first time and made me want to go just to hear the next episode! The storyline is great, the app is easy to use and when the zombies chase you, you can't help but sprint 🤣🤣 Wonderful concept and so glad I found it! The other areas of the app like the 5/10/20km running plans are valuable and building up my base is a fun twist too. I recommend this app to everyone, its honestly the greatest motivator!

So I have tried this on 3 different phones and had the same issue. Audio works for about 10 mins and then app goes silent. Have tried with / without music, internal and external player...no luck. As for not looking at app once started...need to remove that statement. Also, no headset start stop. No doubt the OS will be blamed, so uninstalled cause probably no resolve.

title: Cassowary Independent News
description:
The Cassowary Coast Independent News (CCIN) with a current distribution of 2,600 people across the region. We produce a quality newspaper app that is informative, balanced in its reporting, produces quality journalism and brings cohesion to our community. CCIN will produce a paper that is inclusive of all voices in our community and produce a paper that respects people from all walks of life. The CCIN is a newspaper designed to report the truth of what is happening in the Cassowary Coast Community in an unbiased fashion.  

With the advent of this mobile app we want the process of sharing news and events even more seamless and user friendly on a weekly basis.

Users can become a member, check various News Topics of their choice and view information about local events and happenings, TV guides, Sports activities, rural news, classifieds and even have an option to browse Advertisements options.

We do offer advertising options through our website, and we have also got a trades and services page.

Come join us and enjoy the experience of being in Cassowary Coast

title: NYC Bus Checker
description:
NYC Bus Checker brings you live transit times, smart journey planning and detailed route maps for all of New York. Right to your Android phone or tablet.

With official MTA-licensed support for bus and subway, NYC Bus Checker is the hit app that has you covered, no matter where you need to go in New York.

Main Features

•	Live times at all New York’s 15,000+ bus stops
•	Plan a journey anywhere in NYC by bus, subway, rail and more
•	Get live times on your home screen with the Bus Checker widget
•	Explore 3D route maps for all NYC Bus Routes - see exactly where your bus goes.
•	Download official MTA bus and subway maps - get around underground
•	Never miss your stop again with Stop Alerts 
•	Get real-time CitiBike dock info
•	Be one step ahead with updates on detours, closures and cancellations
•	Save your favorite stops and places for easy access

Press

•	Featured on BBC Click, Telegraph Online, The Independent, Cosmopolitan and Wired UK
•	“If you regularly ride a bus, then you should not leave home without Bus Checker” - The Guardian 

Problems with the app?

Please read through our FAQs on our website www.buschecker.com 

For more help, don’t hesitate to get in touch with our helpful support team on twitter @NYCBusChecker or by email at support@buschecker.com

Notes
-	Bus Checker is a registered trademark of FatAttitude Limited
-	Data provided by official MTA feeds
-	MTA logo and maps are used with permission
-	Bus Checker can send anonymous usage stats and crash reports to us so that we can improve the app; no personally identifiable information is collected or transmitted

comments: A very good app that is usually accurate. Arrival times are closs, though some minutes may be described as biblical ones.

not accurate/update time too slow. There are 2 bus lines on my way to work, one is exress another is local, 3 mins ago the estimate time is 3 mins for the local and 12 mins for the express, during all these 3mins, it's stays like this, but 3mins later it's 3mins for the local and 1 mins for the express. It probably is no big deal for the developer, but I missed the express bus.

it works with 80% success of prediction to schedule... meaning, 80% of the time the bus will be there on the time its predicted (at least for my buses), so very well worth it. i dont think theres a better more comfortable app to use for this. so been using it for years.
Widget works again!! Review is back to 5 stars again. Love this app, very accurate and a must need if you use the buses in NY
I find bus checker to be convenient, accurate and helpful. couldn't be more please.

title: THE VICTORY STATION
description:
THE VICTORY STATION
Excellence in Who We Are 
Radio is what we do. Excellence is who we are. Every day, all day we are LIVE on the air or on the web sharing, inspiring, giving back to our most prized possession…the listeners. For over thirty-seven years, The Victory Station has been privileged to broadcast gospel music, ministry and informative programs.

THE VICTORY STATION
Excellence in What We Accomplish
– Jacksonville’s first full-time gospel radio station since 1979 – Locally owned and operated since December 1989 – A Variety of Traditional and Contemporary Gospel Music for every generation – Free community and church events advertised weekly – Live call-ins for prayer or song requests – Personal touch – live on-air announcers,– Historical and public interest programming to address community and national issues through our sponsorship of Jax Engage, Community Network and Senior Rap Line.

THE VICTORY STATION
Station Profile
– 5,000 Watts – Potential Listeners of approximately 1.8 million – Area Coverage – Northeastern Florida and Southeast Georgia (within 65 mile radius of Jacksonville, FL)


THE VICTORY STATION
Honors & Recognitions
– 2011 Stellar Award Winner for Radio Station of the Year (Medium Market),
- 2007 Stellar Award Nominee for Radio Station of the Year (Medium Market) – 2007 Florida Gospel Announcers Guild Radio Station of the Year - Eartha M.M. White Award of Excellence – Florida Conference of Black State Legislators – Southern Christian Leadership Conference – Arms of Mercy Drug-Free Recovery – Jacksonville Independent Living Program

THE VICTORY STATION
Contributions & Community Involvement
– American Cancer Society – American Diabetes Association – MADD(Mothers Against Drunk Drivers) – Ribault Senior High School – United Negro College Fund – William M. Raines High School – Jacksonville Urban League – Learning for Life – Children’s Wish Foundation – Clara White Mission – Expanding Minds, Inc. – ICARE, Women of Color Cultural Foundation, Edward Waters College, UNF, Annual Thanksgiving Luncheon for Seniors

THE VICTORY STATION
Excellence in What We Do
The Victory Station is known for professional and long-standing business relationships as well as its stability in its market.
Our proficient account executives offer customized advertising programs to grow your business while exposing our audience to new opportunities in the marketplace.

THE VICTORY STATION
How We Can Help
– Competitive advertising packages and broadcasts to fit your budget – Marketing advice to help meet your expectations – Websites Banner Ads

THE VICTORY STATION
Excellence on the Web
Although The Victory Station has been privileged to remain on the airwaves for many years, we are aware of the changing technical climate. Therefore we launched our own website with live stream 24/7 along with our phone app. This additional outlet has expanded our listening audience to a global platform and has afforded us new opportunities in the marketplace.

title: Todoist: To-Do List, Tasks & Reminders
description:
🏆 2020 Editor's Choice by Google
🥇 "Todoist is the best to-do list app right now" - The Verge

Todoist is used by 25 million people to organize, plan and collaborate on projects, both big and small.

Use Todoist to:
• Capture and organize tasks the moment they pop into your head.
• Remember deadlines with reminders and due dates. 
• Build lasting habits with recurring due dates like "every Monday".
• Collaborate on projects by assigning tasks to others.
• Prioritize your tasks with priority levels.
• Track your progress with personalized productivity trends.
• Integrate your tools like Gmail, Google Calendar, Slack, Amazon Alexa and more.

Available on any device, Todoist will quickly become your hub for getting work and life organized.

Why you’ll love it on Android:
• Stay organized from your phone, tablet and watch.
• Drag the Plus Button anywhere to insert a new task.
• Simply type details like "tomorrow at 4pm" and Todoist will recognize it all for you.
• All the power from Android: lock screen widget, Quick Add tile, Assistant, and notifications.

Happy organizing!

• • •

Questions? Feedback? Visit get.todoist.help or reach out on Twitter @todoist.

*About Premium billing*:
If you choose to purchase Premium, payment will be charged to your Google Play account, and your account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period. You can choose to be billed monthly or annually. You can turn off auto-renew in your Google Play settings any time after purchase.

recentChanges: 🐛 You’ll once again see a note at the bottom of your screen when you check something off in task view — if there was a mistake, you can quickly undo it!
comments: It really lacks a calendar view or better integration with Google Calendar (e.g. sync more than one project, add colors to tasks in Google Calendar according to labels or projects, etc.). Otherwise it has been great, I'm really enjoying the app! Sub tasks should show their parent in "Next 7 Days" and "Today", this would be super powerful for splitting a task over several days, it would be a game changer for me!

The new widget does not allow me to open the app directly, like it could before. Updates should never remove features. Knocking my review down - rest of the app is still great. Edit: this feature has indeed been fixed, however I can't raise the score because what drove me here was another bug/update. It seems that my tasks/items aren't visible on the widget. I tried a restart and everything. You can still interact with them, but the widget is just a white blank canvas where tasks should be.

Been using for years, and it worked great until 1 day ago. Lists using widgets on Android all have white text on white background now... So obviously unusable. Must have been in an update as multiple Android users are experiencing the same in the last couple of days.

I bet it would work for someone who mainly needs a list, but personally I need alarms and reminders to keep me on track. I was looking for one when I found todoist that was advertised as having a reminder setting. I was disappointed to find out that the reminder function was a paid function, so I uninstalled the app. I bet it would work for someone else, but not for me

Just downloaded the latest update, to find everything on the widget completely clear. All my project lists gone ! Luckily it's all still within todoist but not on the widget. Still nothing after deleting and setting the widget back up. Looks like I'll have to use the icon again !

comments: Really good app for investing. Relevant information to the way I trade can easily be found and setup, the app itself is fluid, trades are easy to input, and verifying you want a trade to go through is great. One glaring issue I have is updating the favorites list. Sometimes, the favorites list will not update the stocks I want to add. Not able to even create an account. There is bug in the app which needs to be corrected. It is not going ahead after the birthday input in the account creation. I tried installing it after an year. Still the same.. no improvement.. disappointed...

This app is 100% garbage. Trading values are rounded and thus inaccurate and that is if they even pull back data and let you trade at all. The FAQs tell you literally nothing. It will randomly reset your settings or not let your log in at all. I'll be cashing out, closing my account, and moving to Robinhood. There is a reason that one is so popular.

Not really impressed with this app when compared to the dozens of other investing app. Dough doesn't have any instant funding while waiting for funds transfer. The transfer takes longer than other apps I have used. The interface is annoying and buggy with the app sometimes closing while I'm the middle of looking through stocks. This isn't friendly to investors wanting to make money. This is more like an entry level investment platform that someone with no knowledge of investing will benefit.2/5

Incredible App! Customer Service! And most importantly education! These guys KNOW what they are doing and talking about. They offer a host of educational videos on YouTube and often go live to answer questions! Very easy to use and great for beginners. Must download!

title: Housejoy-Trusted Home Services
description:
At Housejoy, we provide you with a variety of at-home services that simplify your everyday living. You can book a wide range of services from home construction to home maintenance, salon-at-home to home cleaning and appliance repairs delivered by well-qualified professionals from anywhere, anytime across 6 Indian cities.

Housejoy home services are available in Bangalore, Hyderabad, Chennai, Delhi, Mumbai, Pune.

Why Housejoy?
- Easy & Quick to book
- Highest Quality Standard
- Hassle-Free Experience
- On-Time Arrival & Delivery
- Certified, Background-Verified experts
- Guaranteed quality of service
- Transparent and affordable pricing
- Trusted by over 2,000,000 Indians!
- Caters to everything from Salon-at-Home Services to Home Construction & Maintenance

Construction Services: Your dream home needs excellent craftsmanship, and who better to give it life than our Top-Class home construction team! On-Time Project Delivery and a Hassle-Free Experience from Plan Approval to Handover Guaranteed. 

Renovation Services: Reinvent your home with our Top-Grade Renovation Services. Book renovation services for any part of the house ranging from bathroom to kitchen. Hassle-Free Experience Guaranteed from Plan to Handover.

Interior Services: Spruce up your living space with our All-New Housejoy Interior Design. Whether you have a 1BHK or a villa, our expertise and High Quality Standard leaves you with a Hassle-Free Experience from Design to Handover.

Salon at home
Our trained beauty experts use top of the line products and provide a range of beauty services like waxing, threading, massage, pedicure/manicure, hair cutting and colouring etc. at the comfort of your home. We also offer a range of beauty packages for skin care, hair care and other beauty services.

Home Cleaning Services
A range of home cleaning packages to suit your needs. You can order for bathroom, bedroom, kitchen deep cleaning, furniture and furnishing cleaning, floor scrubbing and polishing services as well as an all-inclusive Full Home Deep Cleaning.

Appliance Repair & Service at Home
Housejoy appliance repair experts will examine and repair your home appliances in no time. We undertake AC repair and servicing, washing machine repair jobs, TV repairs, Refrigerators repair, Chimney & Hob repair etc.

Painting Services 
Book interior or exterior house painting jobs for homes of all sizes starting at just Rs.7/sq feet.

Pest Control Services at Home
Choose from a set of pest control services like Cockroach control, Rat Control, Ant Control, Termite Control, General pest control etc.

Plumbing Services at Home
Find professional and trained plumbers for all your plumbing troubles like leaking pipes, dripping faucets, bathroom fittings, toilet and sanitary work etc.

Electrical repair services at home
We offer electrical services at home for fitting and removing fans, switchboard installation and replacement, circuit fault finding, all kinds of wiring works, tube lights & other lights fitting and removal etc.

Carpentry Work at Home
Book skilled carpentry services from the app to solve all your furniture installation, assembly and repair problems.

Computer Repair Service at Home
Our efficient and well-qualified laptop & desktop repair engineers will take care of issues like overheating, display issues, speaker issues, screen damage, data recovery, power issues, etc.

Packers & Movers Services
Moving to a new house? We’re a one-stop-shop for all your end-to-end relocation needs - packing, moving, unpacking, cleaning, painting, plumbing, electrical help and the list goes on.

Massages for Men at Home
Need to destress at home? Our qualified therapists will come right to your doorstep! The use of aromatic massage candles will guarantee a rejuvenating experience.

Used, trusted and appreciated by over 1,500,000 happy customers, download the Housejoy App for all your home service needs now

If you have any complaints /suggestions, please write to us at complaints@housejoy.in

comments: I booked services on this app twice. Both times the technician never showed up. Nor is there a way to follow up or get updates. This app is a waste of time. Uninstalled it.

Highly unprofessional behaviour. I had booked from 4-5. The expert alotted calls up and say she is available after 5:30 or 6. She also said to cancel the booking and gave assurance that new expert would be alotted for the required slot. When I do that, the slots are shown booked. Why do they accept the requests if they are not available only. It was such a headache for me because I had to go somewhere in the evening and all other salons were fully booked for that day. Frst nd last experience.👎

Used app for first time, horrible experience. Person didn't had understanding of work assigned. broke my new lock and make shift arrangements were done which broke within one month. on contacting housejoy, no help was provided.

It is not giving an option of typing my address manually. The App detects my location correctly but the address that it generates based on my GPS is not correct.. It shows 3 houses far away house-no. I tried to edit the house-no with the floor-no but not able to do it as it is allowing to set my address only via GPS. Allow users to manually type their address as well because at times the manual entry is more accurate than GPS generated house address.

Waste app.. While booking any serive they will show small amount and the techinican who visits your home will ask 4-5 times higher amount which is shown while booking... If you complain about that also there will not be any response from Housejoy.. For just saying there is a problem in AC stabiliser technician charged 900/- and after he lefts I got a message that the charges for the service is 143/- means he as taken 5 times high amount regarding which I have complained for more than 6 times.

title: Indian Independence Day Wallpapers 4K & Ultra HD
description:
Independence Day is annually celebrated on 15 August, as a national holiday in India.The National Flag of India is a horizontal rectangular tricolor of India saffron, white and India green with the Ashoka Chakra, a 24-spoke wheel, in navy blue at its center.it became the official flag of the Dominion of India on 15 August 1947.

The saffron color symbolizes the sacrifice and selflessness, white color is for truth and purity and green is for youth and energy and the Ashok chakra symbolizes the peace and courageousness. There is the Asoka Chakra in the middle of the white color of the flag.

Let us celebrate & enjoy the freedom to live independently in our country helpfully, peacefully cheerfully, by remembering our National Heroes who gave us Freedom after suffering pain & sacrificing their lives.

title: Crypto Tracker by BitScreener - Live Coin Tracking
description:
Find, track, price alerts, real-time portfolio, charts, news & discussion for all 2000+ cryptocurrencies and Bitcoin ALL-IN-ONE app!

BitScreener streams real-time prices & coinmarketcap from 200+ crypto markets & trading platforms, including Binance, Coinbase Pro, Gemini, Kraken, Huobi, Bittrex, OKEx, Kucoin, BitMEX, Bitstamp,  Bitfinex, Poloniex, Remitano,  HitBTC, etc. (See the full list below)

UNIQUE FEATURES:

***REAL-TIME CRYPTO MARKET***
- Real-time 3000+ crypto prices & coin stats: Bitcoin, Litecoin, Electroneum, Ripple, Ethereum, Dogecoin, Miota (IOTA), etc
- Up-to-second coin market cap, Bitcoin & Altcoins ticker
- Support 200+ crypto market exchanges: 
- Support all trading pairs on any market, such as Ethereum (ETH)/BTC on Binance, Litecoin (LTC)/EUR on Coinbase, XRP/ETH on Bittrex, Electroneum (ETN)/USDT on Cryptopia, etc.

***REAL-TIME CRYPTO PORTFOLIO***
BitScreener is the only app available on App Store that gives you up-to-second profit/loss on your hodl (coin holdings)
- Sync your portfolios with 30+ most popular crypto exchanges to track your investments in real-time
- Support unlimited portfolios & Chart views
- Coming soon: import from any cryptocurrency wallet & exchange like Jaxx, Breadwallet, MyEtherWallet, Mycelium, Toast wallet, Bitpay, Loafwallet, CoinSpace, Xapo, Copay, Abra, Airbitz, Wirex XRP wallet, etc.

***ADVANCED CRYPTO SCREENING TOOL***
One click to find potential coins to invest by many criteria.
- Market Cap, Volume 24h & Price
- Supply, ICO info, Sector & Social
- Performance, ages, type, exchange, etc

***INTERACTIVE & POWERFUL CRYPTO CHARTS***
A high-resolution & full-screen bitcoin & altcoin charts with hundreds of technical indicators.
- Interactive drawing tools
- Support multiple chart types (Candle Stick, Bar, Line), Indicators (ADL, ADX, Aroon, etc.), Overlays (SMA, Bollinger Bands, etc.)

***The #1  CRYPTO ALERT***
Stay on the top of the market with SPECIAL ALERTS that only available on BitScreener
- Recurring price alerts every 15 min, 30 min, 1h & 2h
- Price limit alert
- ALARM option to wake you up at midnight
- Performance 1H, 1D, 1W, 1M, 6M alerts
- Volume 24h, coin cap alerts

***CRYPTO INFO***
- Links to Crypto Exchanges to buy/sell coins
- Full coin profile: website, age, algorithm, Github, etc.

***CRYPTO NEWS & DISCUSSION***
Breaking cryptocurrency news from all reliable sources like Coindesk, etc.

***REAL-TIME CRYPTOCURRENCY CONVERTER & CALCULATOR***
BitScreener is the only app that you can: 
- Calculate real-time quotes: coin to coin, coin to fiat, fiat to coin and fiat to fiat.
- Save & sync your converters on multiple devices

Full list of supported markets: Binance, OKEx, Coinbase Pro, Bithumb, Kraken, Bitstamp, KuCoin, Gate.io, Poloniex, Binance US, BtcTurk PRO, Bitbank, Bitpanda Pro, Coinfloor, Huobi Global, BigONE, FTX, Bittrex, Liquid, BitMax, bitFlyer, EXMO, Gemini, Paribu, eToroX, Bithumb Global, Luno, Zaif, Bitkub, Indodax, CEX.IO, Bitso, OKCoin, Max Maicoin, BitoPro, Nominex, BTCMarkets, Independent Reserve, OKEx Korea, WhiteBIT, HitBTC, Probit, Bitfinex, Livecoin, Hotbit, Coincheck, Bilaxy, AEX, Tokenize, BitMart, Coindeal, Oceanex, WazirX & 200 more coin exchanges.

Disclaimer: BitScreener is not responsible for profits, revenues, or data and financial losses. All the websites or brands mentioned above are not affiliated with BitScreener. This app uses publicly available API from crypto markets and conforms to terms and conditions to perform queries and present data.

title: The Grand Mafia
description:
Are you ready to become the most legendary Mafia Boss?

Since the death of our Old Godfather, the Family has been missing a strong leader, one that can unite all the mafia gangs. You must find and recruit talented individuals from all corners of the underworld society, ranging from thieves and mercenaries to athletes and businessmen, to strengthen your crew. Fight, dominate and become the criminal mastermind who can take over the whole underworld!

[Game Features]:

☆Take Over the Underworld☆

Players will need to take on the law and battle other players to control the cities they reside in. Businesses will be up for grabs. Citizens seeking a better life will look to you as their savior. You will entice models and celebrities to join your life of crime with your dashing looks and mysterious charisma!

☆Lots of Thugs to Choose From☆

There are many different types of thugs within the game. Bruisers, Hitmen, Bikers and Mortar Cars are all at your disposal! Each type of thugs have their own stats. You will need to upgrade your loyal minions and choose the formations of your crews wisely. There will be times when you need to be aggressively offensive, times when you need to be overly defensive, and then there will be times when you need to have stealth on your side!

☆Tons of Faction Events☆

Once you have joined a Faction, you will be able to take part in numerous weekly and seasonal events. Want to take over the local government together? Want to clean up the streets of any unworthy punks who want to criticize your reign of terror? Stay tuned for various cool competitions!

☆Customizable Strategies☆

Every player will be able to develop their criminal empire differently. There are different skills, stats, characters and upgradable content within the game, which require your attention to strategy to individualize your army with fully-fledged mechanics. 

☆Construct, Invest and Date☆

How will you prioritize the development of your criminal empire? Will you take over local businesses? Invest in the right strategic upgrades? Improve the look of your Turf, so that it strikes fear into your enemies? Perhaps you’ll just make everyone around you jealous by dating all the local hotties when they realize you’re the slickest crook in town!

☆Different Styles of Fighting☆

This game offers various types of battles. Sometimes you will need to choose your special characters to tackle harder opponents. At other times you will have to organize massive Crews to invade the turfs of other players. There are be both interactive and idle battles to choose from!

☆Worldwide Online Tournaments☆

You won’t be alone in this pursuit to live a life of a Mafia Boss! You will compete with players from all over the world to reach the top of your criminal career. Will you join forces with them to form a Faction, or meddle in their operations to take them down? Who will become the next godfather? Your actions will determine your fate!


Official Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/111488273880659
Official Line: @thegrandmafiaen
Official e-mail: tgmafia@yottagames.com

●Tips
※ The app is free to download. There is some paid content available via in-app purchases.
※ Please pay attention to your gaming time and avoid addiction.
※ The content of this game involves violence (attacks and other bloody scenes), strong language, game characters wearing clothing of sexual characteristics.

comments: Great game, its a good way to pass the time. Bit difficult to grasp what to do in the beginning but once you get the hang of it then its great fun. 30/10/2020 Um.... what happened guys? This last update you just did has made this game glitchy.... sometimes i cant log into the game and have to delete and re-install... so far its been done 3 times.... not cool at all. Fix the problem please. Thanks.

The game has very good graphics and it could be a lot of fun to play if it didnt have players that harrassed and bully you constantly, I have only played for 1 week and I needed to quit, my group was constantly attacked everyday for 3 days by rich players. And were harrassed in there inboxes and made to feel uncomfortable. For no reason . Alot of people quit in my group , in the last couple days because of this. I will not waist my money on game, with players like this, I am uninstalling app.

Stuck on loading screen since last update or would give 3-4 stars, but already getting bored anyway just another typical forced to join a group to play online and get attacked by other players and forced to spend real money or wait forever to advance once you get to a certain point type game. But at least they haven't forced ads on players yet like most do.

Another update 2020 Oct 29. Game is a mess. Can't open app. Upon uninstall reinstall, app opens momentarily to find others saying app very buggy. App no longer works. Wow. title: Trip Checker
description:
TripChecker is the take-anywhere transit app. Get live bus, subway and train departures plus key travel info for cities around the world, including London, New York, Sydney, Chicago, Washington DC and Baltimore - plus the whole of Great Britain.

See instantly when your bus or train is going to arrive, as well as live journey planning to help you get around. TripChecker also displays instant updates on disruptions, traffic reports and stop alerts.

Download TripChecker today to transform the way you travel.

 • From the makers of BusChecker, as featured on BBC Click, Telegraph Online, The Independent & Wired •

MAIN FEATURES

• Live, updated vehicle departures, direct from official data.
• Real-time GPS map of nearest stops.
• Plan your journey anywhere in the world by bus, tube, rail and more.
• One-tap 'get me home' journey planning.
• Service disruptions including diversions, closures and cancellations.
• Stop Alerts - get woken up when you've arrived at your stop!
• A handy widget lets you view live departure times on your home screen.
• Full 3D route maps for all routes - see exactly where you're heading.
• Live Cycle Hire dock locations and availability in key cities.
• Favorite the places and bus stops you use regularly.

Download Trip Checker today - and never miss that last ride home. Although if you do, we're not paying for your trip!

______________________________________________ 

PROBLEMS WITH THE APP? 
Please uninstall then re-install the app - this resolves the vast majority of issues. For more help, please see our support site or get in touch. (and please try this before leaving bad reviews! We do read every support request we receive) 

______________________________________________ 


NOTES
- Data provided by official feeds as described at www.tripchecker.co
- Trip Checker can send anonymous usage stats and crash reports to us so that we can improve the app; no personally identifiable information is collected or transmitted, but you can opt out of this at any time via the app's settings page.

title: Elvie Pump
description:
Elvie Pump is the world’s first silent wearable breast pump that fits in your bra, and your life. Elvie Pump makes it possible to pump on-the-go, completely hands-free, giving you more time and independence.

This app is for use exclusively with Elvie Pump. Download the app and connect it with your Elvie Pump to monitor milk volume in real time, track pumping history for each breast and control the pump remotely. 

Simply place the small, lightweight pump in your nursing bra, turn it on and press Play on the pump or in the app to start your pumping session. Revolutionary technology eliminates noise so that you can pump silently, in peace. 

Elvie Pump will automatically stop pumping when the bottle is full. Pumping has never been so easy - there are just five parts to clean and it takes seconds to assemble. 

Find out more at elvie.com.

comments: I use the app to keep track of how long the pumps have been running. It has a timer function, but it doesn't turn the pump off when the timer runs out (app developers, this would be a nice addition). The timer puts an alert up on your phone when time is up... if you're not looking at the phone, you don't see the alert when the timer goes off. It is nice to be able to use the app to discreetly pause/stop the pumps if necessary. The volume gauge is a rough estimate only. Not bad overall.

Beautiful, but Useless. Look the idea is to help you keep track and analyze your milk supply. It keeps overriding the ounces I pump and now it decided to add pumped time for November 2020, and March 2021. It's Oct 2020... Rendering all previous data that may have been correct useless. It also has a timmer feature, but also useless since it just runs out, doesn't notify you and the pumps keep pumping. Everytime you try to delete a session you pretty much have to delete it 5 times.
I have to forget and reconnect the pumps to the app every single time, otherwise it can't connect to them anymore at each pumping session.
The app is functional but not great. It often fails to retrieve session details and sometimes can't connect to the pumps.
In theory a good idea. Buggy and always disconnects from my pumps constantly

title: Helpseeker
description:
How we help users:
If you’re experiencing a difficult life situation, we can help you find the most relevant support closest to you. Sort through resources and programs by combining filters such as: services (affordable housing, counseling, parenting), populations (youth, seniors, newcomers) and special focus (disabilities, mental health, addictions). 

Find the help you need, fast.

How we help our service partners:
Our desire is to give people a quick and simple way of finding what they need. If you or your organization exists to help people through difficult life situations, please enroll at www.helpseeker.org. Our partnership programs range from free to paid listings based on the level of information you want to share. 

Features: 
· Location-based search for people looking for social help
· Filtering allows users to find the most relevant service
· No sign-up required for users, privacy is our priority
· Free sign-up for support organizations, paid premium listing available
· Currently focused on organizations in Alberta, Canada

title: Child Support, Expenses & Alimony for Co Parents
description:
- Register in less than 5 minutes
- Submit receipts and expenses with a simple click
- Track and store receipts by taking a picture of the receipt
- Manage payments
- Pay with eCheck / ACH / Direct to bank connections
- Make all, individual or partial payments
- Quickly add expenses & upload receipts
- Completely redesigned for ease of use and seamless connection to web application https://my.supportpay.com


SupportPay enables parents who are single, divorced or living apart to share in the finances associated with raising children. We streamline the complex process of sharing, splitting, and managing child support, alimony & child expenses. Parents can upload expenses and receipts, proving the cost is for the child. Payee's can review expenses for their children and either pay or dispute the charges in app, creating a transparent exchange of child support. Parents now have a certified record of all child / family expenses ensuring protection for all while eliminating the financial conflicts that may arise. With SupportPay, parents can now focus on what matters most, raising happy, healthy children.

NOTE: We are not associated with any state or government child support service or agency and we are not an enforcement agency. We provide an independent application for parents to manage child support and share expenses - directly with each other, eliminating the need for the government to be involved in your personal life. If you are looking for the status of your child support payment from the state then visit your state or county child support agency (DCSS) website. You will not find the status of your payment here. However, you can use SupportPay as an independent application to track your expenses and/or payments as well as a method to manage and share additional expenses such as medical, education and child care expenses - which the government does not manage.

- Submit receipts and expenses with a simple click
- Track and store receipts by taking a picture of the receipt
- Manage payments
- Pay with eCheck / ACH / Direct to bank connections
- Make all, individual or partial payments
- Quickly add expenses & upload receipts
- Completely redesigned for ease of use and seamless connection to web application https://my.supportpay.com


SupportPay enables parents who are single, divorced or living apart to share in the finances associated with raising children. We streamline the complex process of sharing, splitting, and managing child support, alimony & child expenses. Parents can upload expenses and receipts, proving the cost is for the child. Payee's can review expenses for their children and either pay or dispute the charges in app, creating a transparent exchange of child support. Parents now have a certified record of all child / family expenses ensuring protection for all while eliminating the financial conflicts that may arise. With SupportPay, parents can now focus on what matters most, raising happy, healthy children.

comments: The customer support is super helpful & I love the expense tracking. It can be kept for court purposes too! It's helpful for when one of the parties says they didn't get the message or they didn't get the payment. Yes it is $80-$110 (they have a promotion right now) a year but its better then dealing with someone who thinks they are always right.

This is a well thought out app. It can take some time to learn, but it can be learned. The document uploading is in my opinion the most useful features as yet. The customer support is knowledgeable, quick, and cares about the users and their problems. This app has impresses me. I don't usually write reviews, but a good app like this deserves one.

This app has been super helpful in my situation. I regularly use the eCheck feautre and the Merhcant feature to create custom categories. I really like the layout of the dashboard and other sections as well. And the fact that it keeps track of data and documents, plus it can be used in court, adds to the accountability.

I love this app! Many people complain, but I've used it for a year and a half with no problems. I got it because my ex is high conflict & it keeps the emotional abuse down. My opinion is that the negative reviews are from people who are rude to their ex, or are court ordered to use this. It makes our separation easier.

I wasn't sure that this app would actually help my situation, but boy was I wrong! This is my favorite app. Anything you think co-parenting or separated parent will need, this has it. Document uploading, eCheck payments, custom categories. Thank you for having a wonderful, helpful product.

title: YourMasterpieces
description:
Join the Yourmasterpieces community of art lovers, artists, art collectors, art galleries, art educators, students and art curators. Started in 2016, the community now has more than 20K users from 140 countries who buy, create or simply appreciate and encourage handmade non-digital fine art like paintings, sculptures, installation art or provide art services for commissioned works. We are not a typical e-commerce platform but a social network for the fine art community and fine art lovers!

-- Express yourself 

Post pictures of your art collection and express the art story in every post. Apply tags to be easily discovered in search results.

Let people know your life story, your professional experience and your art journey in your profile bio. 

-- Empower yourself

Take your own decisions to buy any piece of art without any middlemen involved. Follow artists or art galleries and be the first one to know when they post something new for sale.

Become an entrepreneur, start your journey today! Build your portfolio and share your profile link anywhere. You may also take a printout of your profile page and use it to apply for jobs, art fairs, art competitions or exhibitions. 

Become an independent seller of your art without any complex seller registrations. We help you in your complete end-to-end sales transaction without charging any commission. 

-- Discover and learn

Like artworks to create your personal art collection so others can check out your interests in your profile.

Search any art style, mediums or techniques to take inspirations from for your next masterpiece.

Search any story and discover people who share similar interests with you in art. Use the feature to search for artists by country to discover art styles of different cultures. 

Appreciation of art is a perception of the viewer. Hence, comments on posts are not allowed and likes' given are anonymous. Feel free to express yourself and share your portfolio with friends, family and professional network to create your fanbase. 

Find us on social media,
Facebook:  https://www.facebook.com/yourmasterpieces/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/yourmasterpieces/

title: LegalZoom Estate Planning
description:
The LegalZoom Estate Planning app is the most effective and convenient way to manage and store your estate plan and life stories all in one place. The app features:
 
**Unlimited Secure Cloud Storage** (Only for legal plan members) 
• Securely store, view, and share your LegalZoom Estate Plan and other important files.
• Safeguard your most precious memories, including videos, photos, and more.
• Collaborate with family, friends, attorneys, and tax professionals to get the information you need when you need it.

**Attorney Consultations** (Only for legal plan members)
With our legal plan, you’ll have access to vetted independent attorneys in our managed network who can offer 30-minute consultations on new legal matters, including:

• Last will, living trust, financial power of attorney
• Marriage and divorce
• Contracts, legal agreements, and lawsuits
• Employee termination, compensation disputes, and employment agreements

**Legal Forms** (Only for legal plan members)
As a legal plan member, you’ll get instant access to more than 160 common legal forms, including non-disclosure and rental agreements and promissory notes. Plus:

• Easy-to-follow instructions that guide you from start to finish
• Attorney document reviews

**Tax Consultations** (Only for legal plan members)
Get answers to your tax, accounting and financial questions with the support of a tax professional.
 
**Easy Tracking**
See at a glance the status of your estate planning documents, so you know exactly what you have left to do and what you can cross off your list.
 
**Manage your account**
Anywhere, anytime, you can easily add or modify files and other account info.

title: Kiwi.com: Best travel deals: flights, trains, cars
description:
Find and book the cheapest trips with Kiwi.com
By connecting nearly a thousand airlines, train, and bus carriers worldwide, Kiwi.com can offer you the cheapest tickets to anywhere on the planet.
 
Best search in the travel industry
Try one quick search and you’ll wish that every travel website had our advanced, easy-to-use search tools.
 
Virtual Global Supercarrier
Our vision is to provide all travelers with the best range of door-to-door travel options, no matter the destination.
 
Flexible tickets
Book with as much flexibility as you want with our unique fare types ticketing. From the cheapest flights to the most cancelation options, Kiwi.com's fare types give you maximum flexibility, and they work across your full itinerary with multiple carriers including those that don't cooperate.
 
Global 24/7 customer support
We offer assistance in 12+ languages and we’re constantly innovating new ways for our customers to manage bookings and answer questions, right in the app, without even needing to contact a call center or wait for an email.
 
What the media says
“Kiwi.com will find you the cheapest international flights.” — Condé Nast Traveler
“So clever that once you understand how it works you cannot help but be impressed.” — Business Insider
“Kiwi.com helps you figure out where you can fly within your budget.” — The New York Times
“Kiwi.com gets the lowest price by finding connections that other search engines wouldn’t even consider.” — Peter Greenberg, Emmy-awarded travel journalist

recentChanges:
Hi there.
Thanks for updating the Kiwi.com app. As always, we're doing everything we can to improve your mobile travel experience.
• We've updated the booking flow, separating it into multiple steps, allowing you to focus more clearly on what's required of you in each step of the process.
• R.I.P. to the numerous bugs we eliminated.
We appreciate you & your feedback. It helps us focus our design and development efforts to provide you with the very best mobile user experience.
comments: Appalling. I paid for a plane ticket which is still stuck on 'pending' many days after my flight has actually left, so I was never sent the tickets! I got to the airport and had to buy new, separate tickets for every step of my journey. The refund section of the app does not work. The company have my money and have done nothing to refund me.

App isn't working now, I think they've pulled the plug and ran away with all the refunds and fees collected. Google needs to ban the people behind this app and company and report them to the authorities. They operate their back office in Eastern Europe, might be another sign of scammers. I've lost hope getting a refund from them.

Oct/2020: more problems with cancelled flights and rescheduling... alternatives were ridiculous, and it's impossible to reach support within acceptable time. Will not use Kiwi again. March/2020: My flight has 2 legs, both cancelled by the airlines, only one of them appear as canceled on my booking, I can't ask a full refund automatically, and was given 24h to request it... Refund is done in Kiwi credit, while companies are actually returning the money... I doubt that support will answer to me...

Pretty useful for manage most of your booking, however, a couple of functions are not showing, so for example to tick off all the necessary acknowledgement boxes you'll still need to log in you account using a laptop or desktop.

I have tried to use this app for the last week and it keeps telling me that "you must be offline" as this is the only app that's not working in my phone and I have also just done the update. Please get this fixed.

title: MyCOR: Church of the Redeemer
description:
With the MyCOR App, you can experience Church of the Redeemer anywhere!

Be the first to know about the most recent content from Pastor Dale O'Shields as well as blog posts, events, and news from all that is going on at Redeemer.

Key Highlights
- Watch or listen to messages from Senior Pastor Dale O'Shields
- Grow spiritually with message study guides, Bible reading guides, and more!
- Take fill-in-the-blanks notes as you listen to live or past messages
- Watch Live video streaming of every weekend and First Wednesday services
- Stay connected with COR through event listings
- Give Online

After you’ve downloaded and enjoyed this content, you can share it with your friends and the world via Text, Facebook, or email.

Church of the Redeemer is a multi-cultural, multi-generational, people loving church with several campuses in the greater Washington, DC area, as well as an Online Campus at church-redeemer.org/onlinecampus. The mission of Church of the Redeemer is to communicate the wonderful news of Jesus Christ. We believe in the power of God’s Word to change lives. We value the practical application of His Word to make a difference in who we are and what we do.

title: T.D. Jakes Motivation - Sermons and Podcast
description:
The Official app of Bishop T.D. Jakes and T.D. Jakes Ministries. Stay connected with audio, video, devotionals, podcasts, books and a variety of resources from Bishop T.D. Jakes. Watch live services from The Potter's House of Dallas, stay updated on The Potter's Touch Video Broadcasts, ManPower Conferences, Woman Thou Are Loosed Conferences, MegaFest Conferences and The International Pastors and Leadership Conferences.

T. D. Jakes is a charismatic leader, visionary, provocative thinker, and entrepreneur who serves as senior pastor of The Potter's House, a global humanitarian organization and 30,000-member church located in Dallas.

T.D. Jakes’ mission is carried out through four distinct channels: global humanitarian outreach, inspirational conference series, media and entertainment ventures, and thought leadership forums.

NOTE: Internet or WiFi connection is required in order for the app to access the audio messages and sermons.
The app is fresh every day: New EEL broadcast, and new EEL radio.

DISCLAIMER:
The developer of this app is not a representative, affiliate or subsidiary of the T.D. Jakes Ministries, but believes in what God is doing through her ministry (which is transforming lives with the gospel of Jesus Christ that is being preached and taught). Therefore any enquiry or request as regards the Bible teachings accessible through this app should be sent to the Joyce Meyer Ministries.

title: স্বাধীনতার ইতিহাস
description:
স্বাধীনতা প্রত্যেক জাতির জন্য একটি গর্বের বিষয়।পরাধিনতা একটি জাতির অভিশাপ যে জাতি পরাধীন থাকে তারা কখণো পৃথীবির বুকে মাথা উচু করে ধারাতে পারেনা।বাঙ্গালী জাতি দীর্ঘ নয় মাসের রক্ত ক্ষয়ী যুদ্বের মাধ্যমে স্বাধীন জাতি হিসেবে আত্নপ্রকাশ করে।এই অ্যাপের মাধ্যমে বাংলাদেশের স্বাধীনতা যুদ্বের ইতিহাস অনেক দীর্ঘ।মুলত স্বাধীন পাকিস্থান হওয়ার পর পূর্ব পাকিস্থান নাম ধারন করে। তখন থেকে এ জাতি নানা বৈষম্যের স্বীকার হয়। এই অ্যাপের মাধ্যমে ১৯৪৭ থেকে 
১৯৭১ সাল পর্যন্ত সকল কিছুর বর্ননা পেশ করা হয়েছে।অ্যাপ্টি ডাউনলোড করলে সহজেই ইতিহাসের সঠিক বর্ননা জানতে পারবেন।
অ্যাপ্টির ভিতর যা রয়েছে সেগুলো হলোঃ
১৯৪৭ সালের বিভিন্ন ঘটনা কিভাবে ভারত ভাগ হল ,দ্বিজাতি তত্ব এবং ব্রিটিশদের বিভিন কূট কৌশল কিভাবে এত বছর ভারত শাষন করেছে সে সব এর ব্যাপক বর্ণনা।
১৯৪৮ সালে ছাত্রলীগ প্রতিষ্ঠা এবং মায়ান মারের পূর্ন স্বাধীনতা লাভ এবং ভারতের অহিংস আন্দোলনের নেতা মহাত্মা গান্ধীর আততায়ীর গুলিতে নিহত হওয়ার ঘটনা। এবং বাংলা ভাষার জন্য আন্দোলন ও স্বধীনতা সংগ্রাম প্রতিষ্টা ইত্যাদি।
১৯৪৯ সালের বাংলাকে পাকিস্থানের অন্যতম রাষ্টভাষ করার দাবিতে পুর্ব বাংলায় রাষ্ট ভাষা দিবস পালিত হয়। এবং কমিউনিষ্ট কারাবন্দীদের অনষন ধর্মঘাট এবং আওয়ামীলীগ প্রতিষ্টা সহ নানা বিষয় জানতে পারবেন।

১৯৫০ সালে পাকিস্থানের নতুন গভর্নর এবং ১ জানুয়ারী শেখ মুজিবর রহমান কে গ্রেফতার  ও বিভিন্ন স্থানে হিন্দু ও মুস্লিম দাঙা সংঘটিত হয়।
১৯৫১ সালে ভাষা আন্দোলনের জন্য বিভিন্ন সংগ্রাম সংঘটিত হয়।
১৯৫২ সালে লিয়াকাত আলী খান ঘোষনা দেন যে পাকিস্থানের রাষ্টভাষা হবে উর্দু এর পর প্রথম ১৪৪ দ্বারা ভেঙে ছাত্রদেরে মিছিল এবং সেখানে গুলি বর্ষণ যা বাঙালি জাতিকে স্বাধীনতার দিকে নিয়ে যায়,বলা হয় ভাষা আন্দোলন ছিল বাঙ্গালী জাতির প্রথম স্বাধীনতা আন্দোলন।
১৯৫৩ সালে বাংলাদেশে স্বাধীনতা আন্দোলনের অন্যতম প্রভাব বিস্তারকারী প্রতিষঠান রাজশাহী বিস্ববিদ্যলয় প্রতিষ্টা লাভ করে। এবং এ বছর আওয়ামীলিগের প্রথম সম্মেলন হয় এনিয়ে রয়েছে বিস্তারিত বর্ননা।

১৯৫৪ সালের প্রাদেশিক নির্বাচন এর যুক্তফ্রন্টের অভুত পুর্ব বিজয় এবং মুস্লিম লীগের ভরা ডুভি আর ও একধাপ বাঙ্গালী জাতিকে স্বাধীনতা আন্দোলনের দিকে নিয়ে যায়।
১৯৫৬ সালে পাকিস্থানের প্রথম সংবিধান প্রনয়ন কপ্রা হয়।এবং বাংলাকে রাষ্ট ভাষা করা হয় এ নিয়ে রয়েছে আলোচনা।
১৯৫৭ সালে কাগমারী সম্মেলন। এবং আওয়ামী লীগ থেকে মাওলানা ভাষানীর পদত্যাগ বাংলাদেশে রাজনীতি অন্যদিকে মোড় দেয় এনিয়ে রয়েছে ব্যাখ্যা বিশ্লেষণ।
১৯৬২ সালের শিক্ষা আন্দোলন।
১৯৬৬ সালের ছয় দফা এবং ১৯৬৮ সালের আগরতলা  ষড়যন্ত্র মামলা এবং এর থেকে মুক্তি ইত্যাদি বিষয়ে ব্যাপক আলোক পাত করা হয়েছে।১৯৬৯ সালের গন অভুথ্যান
১৯৭০ সালের সাধারণ নির্বাচন এং সর্বোপরি ১৯৭১ সালের স্বাধীনতার ইতিহাস এখানে আলোচনা করা হয়েছে। মূলত স্বাধীনতার ইতিহাস বলতে এই দীর্ঘ সঙ্গগ্রাম ও আন্দোলন কে বুঝায়।


অ্যাপ টি আপনাদের কেমন লাগলো অবশ্যই জানাবেন।আর রেটিং দিয়ে পাশে থাকবেন ধন্যবাদ!
অ্যাপ্টির বৈশিষ্টঃ
*একবার ডাউনলোড করার পর অফলাইনে পড়তে পারবেন।
*সহজ ও সাবলীল ডিজাইন।
*যে কোন ডিভাইসে সাপোর্ট দিবে।
descriptionHTML:
স্বাধীনতা প্রত্যেক জাতির জন্য একটি গর্বের বিষয়।পরাধিনতা একটি জাতির অভিশাপ যে জাতি পরাধীন থাকে তারা কখণো পৃথীবির বুকে মাথা উচু করে ধারাতে পারেনা।বাঙ্গালী জাতি দীর্ঘ নয় মাসের রক্ত ক্ষয়ী যুদ্বের মাধ্যমে স্বাধীন জাতি হিসেবে আত্নপ্রকাশ করে।এই অ্যাপের মাধ্যমে বাংলাদেশের স্বাধীনতা যুদ্বের ইতিহাস অনেক দীর্ঘ।মুলত স্বাধীন পাকিস্থান হওয়ার পর পূর্ব পাকিস্থান নাম ধারন করে। তখন থেকে এ জাতি নানা বৈষম্যের স্বীকার হয়। এই অ্যাপের মাধ্যমে ১৯৪৭ থেকে
১৯৭১ সাল পর্যন্ত সকল কিছুর বর্ননা পেশ করা হয়েছে।অ্যাপ্টি ডাউনলোড করলে সহজেই ইতিহাসের সঠিক বর্ননা জানতে পারবেন।
অ্যাপ্টির ভিতর যা রয়েছে সেগুলো হলোঃ
১৯৪৭ সালের বিভিন্ন ঘটনা কিভাবে ভারত ভাগ হল ,দ্বিজাতি তত্ব এবং ব্রিটিশদের বিভিন কূট কৌশল কিভাবে এত বছর ভারত শাষন করেছে সে সব এর ব্যাপক বর্ণনা।
১৯৪৮ সালে ছাত্রলীগ প্রতিষ্ঠা এবং মায়ান মারের পূর্ন স্বাধীনতা লাভ এবং ভারতের অহিংস আন্দোলনের নেতা মহাত্মা গান্ধীর আততায়ীর গুলিতে নিহত হওয়ার ঘটনা। এবং বাংলা ভাষার জন্য আন্দোলন ও স্বধীনতা সংগ্রাম প্রতিষ্টা ইত্যাদি।
১৯৪৯ সালের বাংলাকে পাকিস্থানের অন্যতম রাষ্টভাষ করার দাবিতে পুর্ব বাংলায় রাষ্ট ভাষা দিবস পালিত হয়। এবং কমিউনিষ্ট কারাবন্দীদের অনষন ধর্মঘাট এবং আওয়ামীলীগ প্রতিষ্টা সহ নানা বিষয় জানতে পারবেন।

১৯৫০ সালে পাকিস্থানের নতুন গভর্নর এবং ১ জানুয়ারী শেখ মুজিবর রহমান কে গ্রেফতার ও বিভিন্ন স্থানে হিন্দু ও মুস্লিম দাঙা সংঘটিত হয়।
১৯৫১ সালে ভাষা আন্দোলনের জন্য বিভিন্ন সংগ্রাম সংঘটিত হয়।
১৯৫২ সালে লিয়াকাত আলী খান ঘোষনা দেন যে পাকিস্থানের রাষ্টভাষা হবে উর্দু এর পর প্রথম ১৪৪ দ্বারা ভেঙে ছাত্রদেরে মিছিল এবং সেখানে গুলি বর্ষণ যা বাঙালি জাতিকে স্বাধীনতার দিকে নিয়ে যায়,বলা হয় ভাষা আন্দোলন ছিল বাঙ্গালী জাতির প্রথম স্বাধীনতা আন্দোলন।
১৯৫৩ সালে বাংলাদেশে স্বাধীনতা আন্দোলনের অন্যতম প্রভাব বিস্তারকারী প্রতিষঠান রাজশাহী বিস্ববিদ্যলয় প্রতিষ্টা লাভ করে। এবং এ বছর আওয়ামীলিগের প্রথম সম্মেলন হয় এনিয়ে রয়েছে বিস্তারিত বর্ননা।

১৯৫৪ সালের প্রাদেশিক নির্বাচন এর যুক্তফ্রন্টের অভুত পুর্ব বিজয় এবং মুস্লিম লীগের ভরা ডুভি আর ও একধাপ বাঙ্গালী জাতিকে স্বাধীনতা আন্দোলনের দিকে নিয়ে যায়।
১৯৫৬ সালে পাকিস্থানের প্রথম সংবিধান প্রনয়ন কপ্রা হয়।এবং বাংলাকে রাষ্ট ভাষা করা হয় এ নিয়ে রয়েছে আলোচনা।
১৯৫৭ সালে কাগমারী সম্মেলন। এবং আওয়ামী লীগ থেকে মাওলানা ভাষানীর পদত্যাগ বাংলাদেশে রাজনীতি অন্যদিকে মোড় দেয় এনিয়ে রয়েছে ব্যাখ্যা বিশ্লেষণ।
১৯৬২ সালের শিক্ষা আন্দোলন।
১৯৬৬ সালের ছয় দফা এবং ১৯৬৮ সালের আগরতলা ষড়যন্ত্র মামলা এবং এর থেকে মুক্তি ইত্যাদি বিষয়ে ব্যাপক আলোক পাত করা হয়েছে।১৯৬৯ সালের গন অভুথ্যান
১৯৭০ সালের সাধারণ নির্বাচন এং সর্বোপরি ১৯৭১ সালের স্বাধীনতার ইতিহাস এখানে আলোচনা করা হয়েছে। মূলত স্বাধীনতার ইতিহাস বলতে এই দীর্ঘ সঙ্গগ্রাম ও আন্দোলন কে বুঝায়।


অ্যাপ টি আপনাদের কেমন লাগলো অবশ্যই জানাবেন।আর রেটিং দিয়ে পাশে থাকবেন ধন্যবাদ!
অ্যাপ্টির বৈশিষ্টঃ
*একবার ডাউনলোড করার পর অফলাইনে পড়তে পারবেন।
*সহজ ও সাবলীল ডিজাইন।
*যে কোন ডিভাইসে সাপোর্ট দিবে।

title: Seniors Beginner Workout - 20 Minutes Training
description:
In this 20-minute workout that features exercises for seniors, we lead older adults through a workout featuring a warm up, strength, flexibility, balance exercises and a cool down. Designed specifically for adults over age 50, this workout can be done at home, at work, at the gym—almost anywhere! You'll need a sturdy chair with arms; two equally weighed objects like dumbbells, soup cans, or water bottles; a mat; and a towel. The App also includes instructions on how to modify some of the exercises to meet different needs.

Just because you are 50+ years old, that does not give you the right to stop taking care of your body. It is important for mature adults to continue or begin a healthy lifestyle to live a long and healthy life.

What are some of the benefits seniors can achieve through an exercise program?

As you grow older, an active life is more important than ever. Even as the world tells you it's time to retire, relax, and take it easy, your body is craving for you to keep moving. And though you may be ready to retire from your 9-5, don’t hang up your walking shoes quite yet. The truth is that if you really want to enjoy these golden years and get more quality time from them, your best strategy is to exercise regularly.

This workout for seniors begins with a simple exercise warmup. then we lead you through a series of strength and balance exercises,

The truth is that if you really want to enjoy these golden years and get more quality time from them, your best strategy is to exercise regularly.

This workout for seniors begins with a simple exercise warmup. then we lead you through a series of strength and balance exercises,

INDEX
Sample Workout for Older Adults
summary: You are 50+ yo and looking for a safe workout routine ? this App is for you .
comments: Loved this. I am 42 years and down with severe back pain and a 10 kg overweight. So this app is just perfect for me as I have not yet reached the part where my body hardly moves or I can not sit on floor. But this is absolutely not for senior citizens, they won't be able to do most of these exercises specially those people, who never did it earlier regularly and need to find an app to start. My suggestion, change the target people. Show this app to light workout for beginners.
Like it isn't timed so can go at own pace. Also like the repeated demo with a real person to ensure doing the exercise correctly. Lay out user friendly and right pace for seniors.
Did the developer of this app test the exercises on those 50+, because many of the exercises can't be done by someone 50+ unless they are very fit to start off with.
Not for all seniors. Can't get on the floor.

I'm a senior lady and the last 2 exercises in particular are the hardest. I can't see many elderly and/or disabled people being able to do them. I'm disabled with chronic pain in my back, arms, shoulders and legs, in fact most of my body. I'll keep at it though, and edit my review in a week or so.

title: ArtRabbit - Your guide to art exhibitions & events
description:
ArtRabbit helps you squeeze more art into your life. Got an hour to spare in Berlin? A free afternoon in London? Heading to New York for a long weekend? Find out what’s going on right now, right where you are. From pop-up shows at up-and-coming galleries to world-class exhibitions at major art institutions, ArtRabbit is the best independent contemporary art guide.

Join the ArtRabbit community to make the most of the app. Compile your personal lists of exhibitions you want to attend and track what you’ve already seen. Follow your favourite artists, project spaces and galleries to have their upcoming shows sent directly to your email inbox and get recommendations by leading artists and curators.

ArtRabbit editorially manages the UK, Berlin and New York, so these locations will always be up to date. We also keep tabs on the international art scene. Wherever the art crowd goes, from Basel to Venice, you'll know what's happening in town.


Use ArtRabbit to:

– Find up-to-date information on contemporary art exhibitions and events, large and small, current and upcoming
– See featured lists of the best shows to attend in major cities
– Explore ArtRabbit’s interactive map of events, near you and around the world
– Search listings for exhibitions, venues, artists and event types
– Follow your favourite artists, project spaces and galleries to have their upcoming shows sent directly to your email inbox
– Plan ahead - compile lists of exhibitions you’d like to attend and track what you’ve already seen
– Get directions to exhibitions close to where you are
– Share events with your friends and network, via email and other social channels
– Travel with the art crowd - ArtRabbit keeps tabs with the busiest cities at any time, so you’ll know what’s happening around the world.
– Get a cultural health check: see your art stats for a snapshot of how many exhibitions you've seen in the past week or month
– Book tickets, get membership info or pick up related publications for selected events

comments: I was pleased to come across this app,but somewhat disappointed. Puzzling ux. I can't find many controls etc. Maybe because I'm old, IDK, but the app doesn't seem to offer much. I don't do "enable location" and there are insufficient towns, no manual location input and particularly in the absence of a spatial search (art within 10, 20 miles etc) so you need to keep changing towns. It would help if exhibitions were shown as you pan around.

a horribly user unfriendly app with lots of good "crowd" info. It's geo locate is way off. You need to "register" to mark a exhibition. The epitome of bad app design. So many apps spend too much time on monetizing and not enough on making a user friendly app. The designers need to reach out to the big museums around the world and get some start-up funding that way.
Crashes at startup. I am running latest Android version. I have over 100 apps and this is the first time I see one crashing at startup. Poorly developed. useless.
I love the new art stats! such a good idea. been using the website but will switch to using the app. works fantastic in London! thanks very much
I live in Perth, Australia and this app only caters for Melbourne, nowhere else in Aus Many more cities need to be added for your app to be able to even have a chance

title: Financial Independence
description:
"Financial Independence" is a DAHON Nano Course.

DAHON Nano Courses are Massive Open Offline App Courses (MOOAC) that run on mobile devices, e.g., Android and iOS, and do not require an internet connection. We build them using our open source tool, UsbongKit.

Table of Contents:
1) Main Content
2) How much do you actually need to live
3) How to achieve Financial Independence
4) Lessons from the “Millionaire Next Door”
5) Lessons from the “Cashflow Quadrant”
6) 8 ways to earn income as an Investor
7) Lessons from the “The Richest Man in Babylon: Seven Cures for a Lean Purse”
8) Lessons from the “The Richest Man in Babylon: 5 Laws of Gold”
9) Lessons from Warren Buffett
10) 3 qualities CEOs should have
11) Lessons from the “The Intelligent Investor”
12) Comprehension Check
0) References

Features:
1) Translation (English, Filipino, and Ilonggo)
2) Voice-over narration (English, Filipino, and Ilonggo)

Bonus:
Philippine Local Languages, such as Filipino and Ilonggo, are automatically unlocked for free. This includes the voice-over narration and the translated script. There's not a lot of materials in Filipino and Ilonggo with both of these, so you can use our products to help you with the pronunciation, spelling, vocabulary, and grammar patterns of Filipino and Ilonggo. 

Note:
English can be unlocked for only 0.99USD (price may vary depending on the country).

If you like this product, and would want to support us financially so that we may continue to build more DAHON Nano Courses and LIKHA Multilingual Interactive Storybook Apps, you can purchase and unlock the English language, and/or download and purchase any of our other products. 

Once unlocked, these in-app purchases remain with your account even if you uninstall the app or switch to a different device!

In addition, you'll be helping us spread our enthusiasm for learning languages, especially to those who may not have access to quality education in the Philippines.

title: CareGiver by John Hancock
description:
The John Hancock CareGiver App provides approved independent caregivers a fast, convenient and paperless way to submit care sessions for services provided to John Hancock Long-term care insureds with active claims.
 
The CareGiver App allows you to:
·         Manage care visits online
·         Submit care sessions to your customer for review/reimbursement
·         Access a history of your prior care sessions 
·         Go Paperless!
 
Download the CareGiver app to easily manage and track services provided to your customers. Start and End sessions to track hours of care and create daily care sessions. Each session will be sent directly through the app to your customer for a streamlined end to end process with faster reimbursement to the insured.

title: Fishbrain - local fishing map and forecast app
description:
Over 10 million anglers trust Fishbrain to improve their fishing experience. Fishbrain has over nine million catches logged, which allows you to gain unique insights and to catch more fish. Fishbrain is your personal fishing log, map, and forecasting tool in one app.

Here’s how you level-up your fishing game with Fishbrain.

• Detailed Search Functionality:  Search by the species you want to target near you.  Looking for your PB Bass?  Fishbrain can help you find it.

• Explore Exact Catch Positions:  Have data on your side and get the edge you’ve been looking for.

• Fishing Forecast and Calendar:  Step up your game by knowing the most likely time for fish to bite.  We cover over 130+ species including the most popular Bass, Trout, Catfish, Carp, etc.  All of our information is based on real-life catch data. 

• Top Baits: stop the guesswork.  Optimize each cast by using the right bait, at the right time for the species you want to hook.  

• Personal Statistics: Focus on your journey and find opportunities for improvement.  Log your catches and see a statistics report on your historical performance in the fish finder app. 

• Discover fishing points: Discover new and interesting locations based on popularity, recent catches, and more.

• Join the Conversation: Get fishing tips and gain knowledge from the
Fishbrain community. Get Pro fishing tips on everything: from choosing the best fishing gear to best fishing time and spots near you.

• Keep Track of Anglers: Know who is catching and what they’re catching, see top hotspots on the map. All the best spots around the US realtime: Florida, California, Texas and more.

• Follow and get relevant updates on various fishing methods: ice fishing, sea angling, trolling and many more.

• Family weekend activity: Organize a fishing adventure for your kids, based on pro tips in the app. Let it be their big catch!

• Get Angler Friends: Find fellow anglers on the fishing maps, connect with anglers in your local area -- that’s right, local.

Our free version offers a lot of cool features. For more advanced fishing experience, Fishbrain Pro is available from $9.99/month. You can subscribe and pay through your Google Play account. Your subscription will automatically renew unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.

recentChanges:
Greetings from just below the surface.

We’re always tweaking and fine-tuning Fishbrain to make it easier and better for you to use. This time around you’ll be happy to hear that we’ve crushed a bunch of bugs. And then feed them to the fish.
